"wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_Negative'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Is féidir leis an uirlis Ghinearálta seo sonraí íomhánna AMH a thiontú "
"go formáid DNG.</para><para>Is formáid íomhá RAW gan chailliúint é an "
"Diúltach Digiteach arna chruthú ag Adobe.</para><para>Féach sonraí faoin "
"bhformáid seo ón <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Digital_Negative'>leathanach seo</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttoheif/converttoheifplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To HEIF"
msgstr "Tiontaigh go HEIF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttoheif/converttoheifplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to HEIF format"
msgstr "Uirlis chun íomhánna a thiontú go formáid HEIF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttoheif/converttoheifplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to HEIF format.</"
"para><para>High Efficiency Image File Format (HEIF), also known as High "
"Efficiency Image Coding (HEIC), is a file format for individual images and "
"image sequences. It was developed by the Moving Picture Experts Group (MPEG) "
"and it claims that twice as much information can be stored in a HEIF image "
"as in a JPEG image of the same size, resulting in a better quality image. "
"HEIF also supports animation, and is capable of storing more information "
"than an animated GIF at a small fraction of the size.</para><para>See <link "
"url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/High_Efficiency_Image_File_Format'>High "
"Efficiency Image File Format</link> for details.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Is féidir leis an uirlis Bainisteoir Scuaine Baisce seo sonraí "
"íomhánna a thiontú go formáid HEIF.</para><para>Is formáid comhaid í Formáid "
"Comhad Íomhá Ard-Éifeachtúlachta (HEIF), ar a dtugtar Códú Íomhá Ard-"
"Éifeachtúlachta (HEIC) freisin, le haghaidh íomhánna aonair agus seichimh "
"íomhánna. D'fhorbair an Grúpa Saineolaithe Pictiúr Bog (MPEG) í agus maíonn "
"siad gur féidir dhá oiread faisnéise a stóráil in íomhá HEIF ná in íomhá "
"JPEG den mhéid céanna, rud a fhágann go bhfuil caighdeán íomhá níos fearr. "
"Tacaíonn HEIF le beochan freisin, agus tá sé in ann níos mó faisnéise a "
"stóráil ná GIF beoite ag codán beag den mhéid.</para><para>Féach <link "
"url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"High_Efficiency_Image_File_Format'>Formáid Comhad Íomhá Ard-Éifeachtúlachta</"
"link> le haghaidh sonraí.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojp2/converttojp2plugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To JP2"
msgstr "Tiontaigh go JP2"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojp2/converttojp2plugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to JPEG-2000 format"
msgstr "Uirlis chun íomhánna a thiontú go formáid JPEG-2000"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojp2/converttojp2plugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to JPEG-2000 "
"format.</para><para>This is an image compression standard and coding system. "
"It was created by the Joint Photographic Experts Group committee in 2000 "
"with the intention of superseding their original discrete cosine transform-"
"based JPEG standard (created in 1992) with a newly designed, wavelet-based "
"method.</para><para>See details about this format from <link url='https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_2000'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Is féidir leis an uirlis Bainisteoir Scuaine Baisce seo sonraí "
"íomhánna a thiontú go formáid JPEG-2000.</para><para>Is caighdeán comhbhrú "
"íomhá agus córas códaithe é seo. Chruthaigh coiste an Chomhghrúpa "
"Saineolaithe Grianghrafadóireachta é sa bhliain 2000 leis an aidhm a "
"gcaighdeán JPEG bunaidh bunaithe ar chlaochlú cosín scoite (a cruthaíodh i "
"1992) a athsholáthar le modh nua-dheartha, bunaithe ar thonnta.</"
"para><para>Féach sonraí faoin bhformáid seo ón <link url='https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_2000'>leathanach seo</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojpeg/converttojpegplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To JPEG"
msgstr "Tiontaigh go JPEG"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojpeg/converttojpegplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to JPEG format"
msgstr "Uirlis chun íomhánna a thiontú go formáid JPEG"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojpeg/converttojpegplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to JPEG format.</"
"para><para>The Joint Photographic Experts Group format is a commonly used "
"method of lossy compression for digital images, particularly for those "
"images produced by digital photography.</para><para>See details about this "
"format from <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG'>this page</link>."
"</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Is féidir leis an uirlis Bainisteoir Scuaine Baisce seo sonraí "
"íomhánna a thiontú go formáid JPEG.</para><para>Is modh comhbhrú "
"caillteanais a úsáidtear go coitianta é formáid an Chomhghrúpa Saineolaithe "
"Grianghrafadóireachta le haghaidh íomhánna digiteacha, go háirithe na "
"híomhánna sin a tháirgtear le grianghrafadóireacht dhigiteach.</"
"para><para>Féach sonraí faoin bhformáid seo ón <link url='https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG'>leathanach seo</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojxl/converttojxlplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To JXL"
msgstr "Tiontaigh go JXL"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojxl/converttojxlplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to JXL format"
msgstr "Uirlis chun íomhánna a thiontú go formáid JXL"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttojxl/converttojxlplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to JPEG-XL "
"format.</para><para>JPEG-XL is a royalty-free raster-graphics file format "
"that supports both lossy and lossless compression. It is designed to "
"outperform existing raster formats and thus to become their universal "
"replacement.</para><para>See details about this format from <link "
"url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_XL'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Is féidir leis an uirlis Bainisteoir Scuaine Baisce seo sonraí "
"íomhánna a thiontú go formáid JPEG-XL.</para><para>Is formáid comhaid raster-"
"grafaicí saor ó ríchíosanna é JPEG-XL a thacaíonn le comhbhrú caillteanais "
"agus gan chaillteanas araon. Tá sé deartha chun feidhmiú níos fearr ná "
"formáidí raster atá ann cheana féin agus dá bhrí sin chun bheith ina n-ionad "
"uilíoch dóibh.</para><para>Féach sonraí faoin bhformáid seo ón <link "
"url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_XL'>leathanach seo</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopgf/converttopgfplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To PGF"
msgstr "Tiontaigh go PGF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopgf/converttopgfplugin.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "A tool to convert images to PGF format"
msgstr "Uirlis chun íomhánna a thiontú go formáid PGF"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopgf/converttopgfplugin.cpp:62
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This Batch Queue Manager tool can convert images data to PGF format.</"
"para><para>The Progressive Graphics File is a wavelet-based bitmapped image "
"format that employs lossless and lossy data compression.</para><para>See "
"details about this format from <link url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Progressive_Graphics_File'>this page</link>.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Is féidir leis an uirlis Bainisteoir Scuaine Baisce seo sonraí "
"íomhánna a thiontú go formáid PGF.</para><para>Is formáid íomhá "
"giotánmhapáilte bunaithe ar thonnta é an Comhad Grafaicí Forásacha a "
"úsáideann comhbhrú sonraí gan chailliúint agus caillteanais.</"
"para><para>Féach sonraí faoin bhformáid seo ón <link url='https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Progressive_Graphics_File'>leathanach seo</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttopng/converttopng.cpp:54
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>If conversion to PNG fails, this may be due to the color profile check. "
