"grafaicí í an Portable Network Graphics a thacaíonn le comhbhrú sonraí gan "
"chailliúint.</para><para>Féach sonraí faoin bhformáid seo ón <link "
"url='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portable_Network_Graphics'>leathanach "
"seo</link>.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/bqm/convert/converttotiff/converttotiffplugin.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Convert To TIFF"
msgstr "Tiontaigh go TIFF"

