msgstr "Luchtaitheoir HEIF"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/heif/dimgheifplugin.cpp:58
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "An image loader based on Libheif codec"
msgstr "Luchtóir íomhá bunaithe ar chód Libheif"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/heif/dimgheifplugin.cpp:63
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "This library is not present on your system."
msgstr "Níl an leabharlann seo i láthair ar do chóras."

#: core/dplugins/dimg/heif/dimgheifplugin.cpp:72
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"This library is available on your system with a maximum color depth support "
"of %1 bits."
msgstr ""
"Tá an leabharlann seo ar fáil ar do chóras le tacaíocht uasta doimhneacht "
"datha de %1 giotán."

#: core/dplugins/dimg/heif/dimgheifplugin.cpp:77
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"This library is available on your system but is not able to encode image "
"with a suitable color depth."
msgstr ""
"Tá an leabharlann seo ar fáil ar do chóras ach níl sí in ann íomhá a "
"ionchódú le doimhneacht datha oiriúnach."

#: core/dplugins/dimg/heif/dimgheifplugin.cpp:84
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This plugin allows users to load and save image using Libheif codec.</"
"para><para>High Efficiency Image File Format (HEIF), also known as High "
"Efficiency Image Coding (HEIC), is a file format for individual images and "
"image sequences. It was developed by the Moving Picture Experts Group (MPEG) "
"and it claims that twice as much information can be stored in a HEIF image "
"as in a JPEG image of the same size, resulting in a better quality image. "
"HEIF also supports animation, and is capable of storing more information "
"than an animated GIF at a small fraction of the size.</para><para>Encoding "
"HEIC is relevant of optional libde265 codec. %1</para><para>See <a "
"href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/High_Efficiency_Image_File_Format'>High "
"Efficiency Image File Format</a> for details.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Ligeann an breiseán seo d'úsáideoirí íomhá a luchtú agus a shábháil ag "
"baint úsáide as códac Libheif.</para><para>Is formáid comhaid í Formáid "
"Comhad Íomhá Ard-Éifeachtúlachta (HEIF), ar a dtugtar Códú Íomhá Ard-"
"Éifeachtúlachta (HEIC) freisin, le haghaidh íomhánna aonair agus seichimh "
"íomhá. Forbraíodh í ag an nGrúpa Saineolaithe Pictiúr Bogtha (MPEG) agus "
"maíonn sí gur féidir dhá oiread faisnéise a stóráil in íomhá HEIF ná in "
"íomhá JPEG den mhéid céanna, rud a fhágann go bhfuil caighdeán íomhá níos "
"fearr. Tacaíonn HEIF le beochan freisin, agus tá sé in ann níos mó faisnéise "
"a stóráil ná GIF beoite ag codán beag den mhéid.</para><para>Tá ionchódú "
"HEIC ábhartha don chódac roghnach libde265. %1</para><para>Féach <a "
"href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"High_Efficiency_Image_File_Format'>Formáid Comhad Íomhá Ard-Éifeachtúlachta</"
"a> le haghaidh sonraí.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/heif/dimgheifplugin.cpp:129
#: core/dplugins/dimg/heif/dimgheifplugin.cpp:145
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "High efficiency image coding"
