msgid "An image loader based on Libpgf codec"
msgstr "Luchtóir íomhá bunaithe ar chódc Libpgf"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/pgf/dimgpgfplugin.cpp:78
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This plugin allows users to load and save image using Libpgf codec.</"
"para><para>The Progressive Graphics File (PGF) is an efficient image file "
"format, that is based on a fast, discrete wavelet transform with progressive "
"coding features. PGF can be used for lossless and lossy compression. It is "
"most suitable for natural images. PGF can be used as a very efficient and "
"fast replacement of JPEG-2000.</para><para>See <a href='https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Progressive_Graphics_File'>Progressive Graphics File documentation</"
"a> for details.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Ligeann an breiseán seo d'úsáideoirí íomhá a luchtú agus a shábháil ag "
"baint úsáide as cód Libpgf.</para><para>Is formáid comhaid íomhá éifeachtach "
"é an Comhad Grafaicí Forásacha (PGF), atá bunaithe ar chlaochlú tonnta tapa, "
"discréideach le gnéithe códaithe forásacha. Is féidir PGF a úsáid le "
"haghaidh comhbhrú gan chailliúint agus caillteanais. Is fearr a oireann sé "
"d'íomhánna nádúrtha. Is féidir PGF a úsáid mar ionadach an-éifeachtach agus "
"tapa ar JPEG-2000.</para><para>Féach <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Progressive_Graphics_File'>doiciméadú Comhad Grafaicí Forásacha</a> le "
"haghaidh sonraí.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/pgf/dimgpgfplugin.cpp:106
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Progressive Graphics File"
msgstr "Comhad Grafaicí Forásacha"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/png/dimgpngexportsettings.cpp:62
#, kde-format
msgid "PNG compression:"
msgstr "Comhbhrú PNG:"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/png/dimgpngexportsettings.cpp:64
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>The compression value for PNG images:</p><p><b>1</b>: low compression "
"(large file size but short compression duration - default)<br><b>5</b>: "
"medium compression<br><b>9</b>: high compression (small file size but long "
"compression duration)</p><p><b>Note: PNG is always a lossless image "
"compression format.</b></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>An luach comhbhrúite d'íomhánna PNG:</p><p><b>1</b>: comhbhrú íseal (méid "
"comhaid mór ach fad comhbhrúite gearr - réamhshocrú)<br><b>5</b>: comhbhrú "
"meánach<br><b>9</b>: comhbhrú ard (méid comhaid beag ach fad comhbhrúite "
"fada)</p><p><b>Tabhair faoi deara: Is formáid comhbhrúite íomhá gan "
"chailliúint í PNG i gcónaí.</b></p>"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/png/dimgpngplugin.cpp:43
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "PNG loader"
msgstr "Luchtaitheoir PNG"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/png/dimgpngplugin.cpp:58
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "An image loader based on Libpng codec"
msgstr "Luchtóir íomhá bunaithe ar chód Libpng"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/png/dimgpngplugin.cpp:63
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This plugin allows users to load and save image using Libpng codec.</"
"para><para>Portable Network Graphics (PNG) is a raster-graphics file-format "
"that supports lossless data compression. PNG was developed as an improved, "
"non-patented replacement for Graphics Interchange Format.</para><para>See <a "
"href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portable_Network_Graphics'>Portable "
"Network Graphics documentation</a> for details.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Ligeann an breiseán seo d'úsáideoirí íomhá a luchtú agus a shábháil ag "
"baint úsáide as códc Libpng.</para><para>Is formáid comhaid raster-grafaicí "
"í Portable Network Graphics (PNG) a thacaíonn le comhbhrú sonraí gan "
"chailliúint. Forbraíodh PNG mar ionadach feabhsaithe, neamhphaitinnithe ar "
"an bhFormáid Idirmhalartaithe Grafaicí.</para><para>Féach <a href='https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portable_Network_Graphics'>doiciméadacht Portable "
"Network Graphics</a> le haghaidh sonraí.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/png/dimgpngplugin.cpp:114
