#: core/dplugins/dimg/raw/dimgrawplugin.cpp:63
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This plugin allows users to load and save image using Libraw codec.</"
"para><para>A camera raw image file contains minimally processed data from "
"the image sensor of either a digital camera, a motion picture film scanner, "
"or other image scanner. Raw files are not yet processed and therefore are "
"not ready to be printed or edited with a bitmap graphics editor. RAW are "
"processed by a raw converter in a wide-gamut internal color space where "
"precise adjustments can be made before conversion to a TIFF or JPEG for "
"storage, printing, or further manipulation. This often encodes the image in "
"a device-dependent color space.</para><para>See <a href='https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Raw_image_format'>Raw Image File documentation</a> for "
"details.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Ligeann an breiseán seo d'úsáideoirí íomhá a luchtú agus a shábháil ag "
"baint úsáide as códc Libraw.</para><para>Tá sonraí íosta-phróiseáilte i "
"gcomhad íomhá ceamara amh ó braiteoir íomhá ceamara digiteach, scanóir "
"scannán gluaisne, nó scanóir íomhá eile. Níl comhaid amha próiseáilte fós "
"agus dá bhrí sin níl siad réidh le priontáil ná le heagarthóireacht le "
"heagarthóir grafaicí giotánmhap. Próiseálann tiontaire amh comhaid amha i "
"spás dathanna inmheánach leathan-gamut áit ar féidir coigeartuithe beachta a "
"dhéanamh sula ndéantar tiontú go TIFF nó JPEG le haghaidh stórála, "
"priontála, nó tuilleadh ionramhála. Is minic a ionchódaíonn sé seo an íomhá "
"i spás dathanna atá ag brath ar fheiste.</para><para>Féach <a href='https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raw_image_format'>dhoiciméadú Comhaid Íomhá Amha</a> "
"le haghaidh sonraí.</para>"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/raw/dimgrawplugin.cpp:117
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: can write file format"
msgid "no"
msgstr "níl"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/tiff/dimgtiffexportsettings.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgid "Compress TIFF files"
msgstr "Comhbhrúigh comhaid TIFF"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/tiff/dimgtiffexportsettings.cpp:59
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Toggle compression for TIFF images.</p><p>If this option is enabled, the "
"final size of the TIFF image is reduced.</p><p>A lossless compression format "
"(Deflate) is used to save the file.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Athraigh an comhbhrú le haghaidh íomhánna TIFF.</p><p>Má tá an rogha seo "
"cumasaithe, laghdaítear méid deiridh íomhá TIFF.</p><p>Úsáidtear formáid "
"comhbhrú gan chailliúint (Díbhoilsciú) chun an comhad a shábháil.</p>"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/tiff/dimgtiffplugin.cpp:43
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "TIFF loader"
msgstr "Luchtóir TIFF"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/tiff/dimgtiffplugin.cpp:58
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "An image loader based on Libtiff codec"
msgstr "Luchtóir íomhá bunaithe ar chód Libtiff"

#: core/dplugins/dimg/tiff/dimgtiffplugin.cpp:63
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"<para>This plugin allows users to load and save image using Libtiff codec.</"
"para><para>Tagged Image File Format, abbreviated TIFF or TIF, is a computer "
"file format for storing raster graphics images, popular among graphic "
"artists, the publishing industry, and photographers. TIFF is widely "
"supported by scanning, faxing, word processing, optical character "
"recognition, image manipulation, desktop publishing, and page-layout "
"applications.</para><para>See <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"TIFF'>Tagged Image File Format documentation</a> for details.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Ligeann an breiseán seo d’úsáideoirí íomhá a luchtú agus a shábháil ag "
"baint úsáide as códac Libtiff.</para><para>Is formáid comhaid ríomhaire í "
"Formáid Comhaid Íomhá Clibeáilte, ar a dtugtar TIFF nó TIF mar ghiorrúchán, "
"chun íomhánna grafaicí rastair a stóráil, atá coitianta i measc ealaíontóirí "
"grafacha, an tionscal foilsitheoireachta, agus grianghrafadóirí. Tacaítear "
"go forleathan le TIFF trí scanadh, facsáil, próiseáil focal, aithint optúil "
"carachtar, ionramháil íomhá, foilsitheoireacht deisce, agus feidhmchláir "
"leagan amach leathanaigh.</para><para>Féach <a href='https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/TIFF'>doiciméadacht Formáid Comhaid Íomhá Clibeáilte</a> le "
"haghaidh sonraí.</para>"

