#: core/dplugins/editor/colors/autocorrection/autocorrectiontool.cpp:110
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>Auto Levels</b>:<p>This option maximizes the tonal range in the Red, "
"Green, and Blue channels. It searches the image shadow and highlight limit "
"values and adjusts the Red, Green, and Blue channels to a full histogram "
"range.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Leibhéil Uathoibríocha</b>:<p>Uasmhéadaíonn an rogha seo an raon toin sna "
"bealaí Dearga, Glasa agus Gorma. Cuardaíonn sé luachanna teorann scáth agus "
"aird na híomhá agus coigeartaíonn sé na bealaí Dearga, Glasa agus Gorma go "
"raon iomlán histeagram.</p>"

#: core/dplugins/editor/colors/autocorrection/autocorrectiontool.cpp:118
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>Normalize</b>:<p>This option scales brightness values across the active "
"image so that the darkest point becomes black, and the brightest point "
"becomes as bright as possible without altering its hue. This is often a "
"\"magic fix\" for images that are dim or washed out.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Gnáthú</b>:<p>Scálann an rogha seo luachanna gile ar fud na híomhá "
"gníomhaí ionas go n-éiríonn an pointe is dorcha dubh, agus go n-éiríonn an "
"pointe is gile chomh geal agus is féidir gan a dath a athrú. Is minic gur "
"\"réiteach draíochta\" é seo d'íomhánna atá doiléir nó nite amach.</p>"

#: core/dplugins/editor/colors/autocorrection/autocorrectiontool.cpp:128
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>Equalize</b>:<p>This option adjusts the brightness of colors across the "
"active image so that the histogram for the value channel is as nearly as "
"possible flat, that is, so that each possible brightness value appears at "
"about the same number of pixels as each other value. Sometimes Equalize "
"works wonderfully at enhancing the contrasts in an image. Other times it "
"gives garbage. It is a very powerful operation, which can either work "
"miracles on an image or destroy it.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Cothromú</b>:<p>Coigeartaíonn an rogha seo gile na ndathanna ar fud na "
"híomhá gníomhaí ionas go mbeidh an histogram don chainéal luacha chomh "
"cothrom agus is féidir, is é sin, ionas go mbeidh gach luach gile féideartha "
"le feiceáil ag an líon céanna picteilíní agus gach luach eile. Uaireanta "
"oibríonn Cothromú go hiontach chun na codarsnachtaí in íomhá a fheabhsú. "
"Uaireanta eile tugann sé drochthoradh. Is oibríocht an-chumhachtach í, ar "
"féidir léi míorúiltí a dhéanamh ar íomhá nó í a scrios.</p>"

#: core/dplugins/editor/colors/autocorrection/autocorrectiontool.cpp:140
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>Stretch Contrast</b>:<p>This option enhances the contrast and brightness "
"of the RGB values of an image by stretching the lowest and highest values to "
"their fullest range, adjusting everything in between.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Codarsnacht Shínte</b>:<p>Feabhsaíonn an rogha seo codarsnacht agus gile "
"luachanna RGB íomhá trí na luachanna is ísle agus is airde a shíneadh go dtí "
"a raon is iomláine, ag coigeartú gach rud eatarthu.</p>"

#: core/dplugins/editor/colors/autocorrection/autocorrectiontool.cpp:148
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<b>Auto Exposure</b>:<p>This option enhances the contrast and brightness of "
"the RGB values of an image to calculate optimal exposition and black level "
"using image histogram properties.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Nochtadh Uathoibríoch</b>:<p>Feabhsaíonn an rogha seo codarsnacht agus "
"gile luachanna RGB íomhá chun an nochtadh agus an leibhéal dubh is fearr a "
"ríomh ag baint úsáide as airíonna histeagram na híomhá.</p>"

#: core/dplugins/editor/colors/autocorrection/autocorrectiontoolplugin.cpp:60
