"automatically. This function requires to have some residual orange mask "
"around the exposed area of the negative."
msgstr ""
"Má bhrúnn tú an cnaipe seo, ríomhtar an pointe bán go huathoibríoch ó "
"shonraí na híomhá. Éilíonn an fheidhm seo go mbeadh roinnt masc oráiste "
"fágtha timpeall ar an limistéar nochta den diúltach."

#: core/dplugins/editor/colors/film/filmtool.cpp:241
#, kde-format
msgid "Exposure correction."
msgstr "Ceartú nochta."

#: core/dplugins/editor/colors/film/filmtool.cpp:242
