msgstr "Céatadán Doiléire Gathach:"

#: core/dplugins/editor/enhance/healingclone/healingclonetool.cpp:132
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A percent of 0 has no effect, values above 0 represent a factor for mixing "
"the destination color with source color this is done radially i.e. the inner "
"part of the brush radius is totally from source and mixing with destination "
"is done gradually till the outer part of the circle."
msgstr ""
"Níl aon éifeacht ag céatadán de 0, léiríonn luachanna os cionn 0 fachtóir "
"chun dath an cheann scríbe a mheascadh leis an dath foinse, déantar é seo go "
"gathach i.e. tá an chuid istigh de gha an scuaibe go hiomlán ón bhfoinse "
"agus déantar an meascadh leis an gceann scríbe de réir a chéile go dtí an "
"chuid sheachtrach den chiorcal."

