msgstr ""
"Cumasaigh an rogha seo chun picteilíní a chaomhnú a bhfuil a ndath gar do "
"thon craicinn."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:312
#, kde-format
msgid "Overall rigidity of the seams:"
msgstr "Dlúsacht fhoriomlán na seams:"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:316
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Use this value to give a negative bias to the seams which are not straight. "
"May be useful to prevent distortions in some situations, or to avoid "
"artifacts from pixel skipping (it is better to use low values in such case). "
"This setting applies to the whole selected layer if no rigidity mask is "
"used. Note: the bias is proportional to the difference in the transversal "
"coordinate between each two successive points, elevated to the power of 1.5, "
"and summed up for the whole seam."
msgstr ""
"Úsáid an luach seo chun claonadh diúltach a thabhairt do na seams nach "
"bhfuil díreach. D’fhéadfadh sé a bheith úsáideach chun saobhadh a chosc i "
"gcásanna áirithe, nó chun déantáin ó scipeáil picteilíní a sheachaint (is "
"fearr luachanna ísle a úsáid i gcás den sórt sin). Baineann an socrú seo "
"leis an tsraith roghnaithe ar fad mura n-úsáidtear masc dolúbthachta. "
"Tabhair faoi deara: tá an claonadh comhréireach leis an difríocht sa "
"chomhordanáid thrasnach idir gach dhá phointe as a chéile, ardaithe go dtí "
"cumhacht 1.5, agus suimithe don seam ar fad."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:325
#, kde-format
msgid "Maximum number of transversal steps:"
msgstr "Uasmhéid céimeanna trasnacha:"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:329
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you choose the maximum transversal step that the pixels in "
"the seams can take. In the standard algorithm, corresponding to the default "
"value step = 1, each pixel in a seam can be shifted by at most one pixel "
"with respect to its neighbors. This implies that the seams can form an angle "
"of at most 45 degrees with respect to their base line. Increasing the step "
"value lets you overcome this limit, but may lead to the introduction of "
"artifacts. In order to balance the situation, you can use the rigidity "
"setting."
msgstr ""
"Ligeann an rogha seo duit an céim thrasnach uasta is féidir leis na "
"picteilíní sna seams a ghlacadh a roghnú. Sa halgartam caighdeánach, a "
"fhreagraíonn don luach réamhshocraithe céim = 1, is féidir gach picteilín i "
"seam a bhogadh picteilín amháin ar a mhéad i gcomparáid lena chomharsana. "
"Tugann sé seo le fios gur féidir leis na seams uillinn 45 céim ar a mhéad a "
"chruthú i gcomparáid lena mbonnlíne. Trí luach na céime a mhéadú, is féidir "
"leat an teorainn seo a shárú, ach d'fhéadfadh sé go dtiocfadh déantáin "
"isteach. Chun an cás a chothromú, is féidir leat an socrú dolúbthachta a "
"úsáid."

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:339
#, kde-format
msgid "Side switch frequency:"
msgstr "Minicíocht lasc taobh:"

#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/contentawareresize/contentawareresizetool.cpp:343
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"During the carving process, at each step the optimal seam to be carved is "
"chosen based on the relevance value for each pixel. However, in the case "
"where two seams are equivalent (which may happen, for instance, when large "
"portions of the image have the same color), the algorithm always chooses the "
"seams from one side.  In some cases, this can pose problems, e.g. an object "
"centered in the original image might not be centered in the resulting image. "
"In order to overcome this effect, this setting allows the favored side to be "
"switched automatically during rescaling, at the cost of slightly worse "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"Le linn an phróisis snoíodóireachta, roghnaítear an uaim is fearr le "
"snoíodóireacht ag gach céim bunaithe ar luach ábharthachta gach picteilín. "
"Mar sin féin, i gcás ina bhfuil dhá uaim coibhéiseach (rud a d'fhéadfadh "
"tarlú, mar shampla, nuair a bhíonn an dath céanna ar chodanna móra den "
"íomhá), roghnaíonn an algartam na huaimeanna ó thaobh amháin i gcónaí. I "
"gcásanna áirithe, is féidir fadhbanna a chruthú leis seo, m.sh., b'fhéidir "
"nach mbeadh réad atá lárnaithe san íomhá bhunaidh lárnaithe san íomhá mar "
"thoradh air. Chun an éifeacht seo a shárú, ceadaíonn an socrú seo an taobh "
"is fearr a athrú go huathoibríoch le linn athscálú, ar chostas feidhmíochta "
"beagán níos measa."

