#: core/dplugins/editor/transform/ratiocrop/ratiocroptool.cpp:232
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Select your constrained aspect ratio for cropping. Aspect Ratio Crop tool "
"uses a relative ratio. That means it is the same if you use centimeters or "
"inches and it does not specify the physical size.</p><p>You can see below a "
"correspondence list of traditional photographic paper sizes and aspect ratio "
"crop:</p><p><b>2:3</b>: 10x15cm, 20x30cm, 30x45cm, 4x6\", 8x12\", 12x18\", "
"16x24\", 20x30\"</p><p><b>3:4</b>: 6x8cm, 15x20cm, 18x24cm, 30x40cm, "
"3.75x5\", 4.5x6\", 6x8\", 7.5x10\", 9x12\"</p><p><b>4:5</b>: 20x25cm, "
"40x50cm, 8x10\", 16x20\"</p><p><b>5:7</b>: 15x21cm, 30x42cm, 5x7\"</"
"p><p><b>7:10</b>: 21x30cm, 42x60cm, 3.5x5\"</p><p><b>8:5</b>: common wide-"
"screen monitor (as 1680x1050)</p><p><b>2:1</b>, <b>3:1</b>, <b>4:1</b>: "
"common panoramic sizes</p><p><b>16:9</b>: common tv-screen (as HDTV or Full-"
"HD)</p><p>The paper <b>Format DIN A</b> use the ratio 1:1.414</p><p>The "
"<b>Golden Ratio</b> is 1:1.618. A composition following this rule is "
"considered visually harmonious but may not be suitable to print on standard "
"photographic paper.</p><p>The <b>Current Aspect Ratio</b> takes aspect ratio "
"from the currently opened image.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Roghnaigh do chóimheas gné srianta le haghaidh bearradh. Úsáideann uirlis "
"Bearradh Cóimheas Gné cóimheas coibhneasta. Ciallaíonn sé sin go bhfuil sé "
"mar an gcéanna má úsáideann tú ceintiméadair nó orlaigh agus mura sonraítear "
"an méid fisiceach.</p><p>Is féidir leat liosta comhfhreagrais de mhéideanna "
"páipéir grianghrafadóireachta traidisiúnta agus barr cóimheas gné a "
"fheiceáil thíos:</p><p><b>2:3</b>: 10x15cm, 20x30cm, 30x45cm, 4x6\", 8x12\", "
"12x18\", 16x24\", 20x30\"</p><p><b>3:4</b>: 6x8cm, 15x20cm, 18x24cm, "
"30x40cm, 3.75x5\", 4.5x6\", 6x8\", 7.5x10\", 9x12\"</p><p><b>4:5</b>: "
"20x25cm, 40x50cm, 8x10\", 16x20\"</p><p><b>5:7</b>: 15x21cm, 30x42cm, 5x7\"</"
"p><p><b>7:10</b>: 21x30cm, 42x60cm, 3.5x5\"</p><p><b>8:5</b>: monatóir "
"scáileáin leathan coitianta (mar 1680x1050)</p><p><b>2:1</b>, <b>3:1</b>, "
"<b>4:1</b>: méideanna panorámacha coitianta</p><p><b>16:9</b>: scáileán "
"teilifíse coitianta (mar HDTV nó Full-HD)</p><p>Úsáideann an páipéar "
"<b>Formáid DIN A</b> an cóimheas 1:1.414</p><p>Is é 1:1.618 an <b>Cóimheas "
"Órga</b>. Meastar go bhfuil comhdhéanamh a leanann an riail seo comhchuí ó "
"thaobh amhairc de ach b'fhéidir nach mbeadh sé oiriúnach le priontáil ar "
"pháipéar grianghrafadóireachta caighdeánach.</p><p>Tógann an <b>Cóimheas Gné "
"Reatha</b> cóimheas gné ón íomhá atá oscailte faoi láthair.</p>"

