msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"This tool allows users to changes plenty of metadata from items.<br><br>Most "
"common Exif, Iptc, and Xmp tags used in photography are listed for editing "
"with standardized values.<br><br>For photo agencies, pre-configured subjects "
"can be used to describe the items contents based on Iptc reference codes."
msgstr ""
"Leis an uirlis seo, is féidir le húsáideoirí go leor meiteashonraí a athrú ó "
"mhíreanna.<br><br>Liostaítear na clibeanna Exif, Iptc, agus Xmp is coitianta "
"a úsáidtear sa ghrianghrafadóireacht le haghaidh eagarthóireachta le "
"luachanna caighdeánaithe.<br><br>I gcás gníomhaireachtaí "
"grianghrafadóireachta, is féidir ábhair réamhchumraithe a úsáid chun cur "
"síos a dhéanamh ar ábhar na míreanna bunaithe ar chóid tagartha Iptc."

