"Uasmhéadaigh gnéithe íomhá (codarsnacht, sáithiú, . . .) le bheith chomh "
"domhanda agus is féidir."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:113
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Set automatic level selection (maximized) for pyramid blending, i.e. "
"optimize image features (contrast, saturation, . . .) to be as global as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh roghnú leibhéil uathoibríoch (uasmhéadaithe) le haghaidh cumasc "
"pirimide, i.e. gnéithe íomhá (codarsnacht, sáithiú, . . .) a bharrfheabhsú "
"le bheith chomh domhanda agus is féidir."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:116
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider Enfuse settings"
msgid "Image Features Balance:"
msgstr "Cothromaíocht Gnéithe Íomhá:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:121
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Balances between local features (small number) or global features (high "
"number)."
msgstr ""
"Cothromaíochtaí idir gnéithe áitiúla (líon beag) nó gnéithe domhanda (líon "
"ard)."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:123
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Set the number of levels for pyramid blending. Balances towards local "
"features (small number) or global features (high number). Additionally, a "
"low number trades off quality of results for faster execution time and lower "
"memory usage."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh líon na leibhéal le haghaidh cumasc pirimide. Cothromaíonn sé i "
"dtreo gnéithe áitiúla (uimhir bheag) nó gnéithe domhanda (uimhir ard). Ina "
"theannta sin, déanann uimhir íseal neamhaird ar cháilíocht na dtorthaí ar "
"mhaithe le ham forghníomhaithe níos tapúla agus úsáid chuimhne níos ísle."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:128
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Hard Mask"
msgstr "Masc Crua"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:130
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Useful only for focus stack to improve sharpness."
msgstr "Úsáideach le haghaidh cruach fócais amháin chun géire a fheabhsú."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:132
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Force hard blend masks without averaging on finest scale. This is only "
"useful for focus stacks with thin and high contrast features. It improves "
"sharpness at the expense of increased noise."
msgstr ""
"Fórsáil maisc chumasc chrua gan meánú ar an scála is fearr. Níl sé seo "
"úsáideach ach amháin le haghaidh cruacha fócais le gnéithe tanaí agus "
"ardchodarsnachta. Feabhsaíonn sé géire ar chostas torainn mhéadaithe."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:137
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider Enfuse settings"
msgid "Well-Exposedness Contribution:"
msgstr "Ranníocaíocht Nochtadh Maith:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:142
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Contribution of well exposed pixels to the blending process."
msgstr "Rannchuidiú picteilíní dea-nochtaithe leis an bpróiseas cumaisc."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:144
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Set the well-exposedness criterion contribution for the blending process. "
"Higher values will favor well-exposed pixels."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh an critéar maidir le dea-nochtadh a chur leis an bpróiseas cumasc. "
"Tabharfaidh luachanna níos airde fabhar do phicteilíní dea-nochtaithe."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:147
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider enfuse settings"
msgid "High-Saturation Contribution:"
msgstr "Ranníocaíocht Sáithithe Ard:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:153
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Contribution of highly saturated pixels to the blending process."
msgstr "Rannchuidiú picteilíní an-sháithithe leis an bpróiseas cumasc."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:155
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Increasing this value makes pixels with high saturation contribute more to "
"the final output."
msgstr ""
"Má mhéadaítear an luach seo, cuirfidh picteilíní a bhfuil sáithiúlacht ard "
"acu níos mó leis an aschur deiridh."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:158
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider enfuse settings"
msgid "High-Contrast Contribution:"
msgstr "Ranníocaíocht Ardchodarsnachta:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:164
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Contribution of highly contrasted pixels to the blending process."
msgstr "Rannchuidiú picteilíní ardchodarsnachta leis an bpróiseas cumasc."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:166
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Sets the relative weight of high-contrast pixels. Increasing this weight "
"makes pixels with neighboring differently colored pixels contribute more to "
"the final output. Particularly useful for focus stacks."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn sé meáchan coibhneasta picteilíní ardchodarsnachta. Má mhéadaítear "
"an meáchan seo, cuirfidh picteilíní le picteilíní comharsanacha de dhathanna "
"difriúla níos mó leis an aschur deiridh. Tá sé seo an-úsáideach le haghaidh "
"cruacha fócais."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:170
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Use Color Appearance Model (CIECAM02)"
msgstr "Úsáid Samhail Dealramh Datha (CIECAM02)"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:172
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Convert to CIECAM02 color appearance model during the blending process "
"instead of RGB."
msgstr ""
"Tiontaigh go samhail cuma datha CIECAM02 le linn an phróisis chumasc in "
"ionad RGB."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/blendingdlg/enfusesettings.cpp:174
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Use Color Appearance Modelling (CIECAM02) to render detailed colors. Your "
"input files should have embedded ICC profiles. If no ICC profile is present, "
"sRGB color space will be assumed. The difference between using this option "
"and default color blending algorithm is very slight, and will be most "
"noticeable when you need to blend areas of different primary colors together."
msgstr ""
"Bain úsáid as Samhaltú Dealramh Datha (CIECAM02) chun dathanna mionsonraithe "
"a rindreáil. Ba chóir go mbeadh próifílí ICC leabaithe i do chomhaid "
"ionchuir. Mura bhfuil aon phróifíl ICC i láthair, glacfar leis go bhfuil "
"spás datha sRGB ann. Tá an difríocht idir an rogha seo a úsáid agus an t-"
"algartam cumasc dathanna réamhshocraithe an-bheag, agus beidh sé is suntasaí "
"nuair is gá duit limistéir de phríomhdhathanna éagsúla a chumasc le chéile."

