"Cabhróidh an cúntóir seo leat a chumrú conas íomhánna a allmhairiú sula "
"gcuirfidh tú iad le chéile in aon cheann amháin."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/expoblending/wizard/expoblendingintropage.cpp:76
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Bracketed images must be taken with the same camera, in the same conditions, "
"and if possible using a tripod."
