"huathoibríoch nuair a thosaíonn an feidhmchlár"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/mjpegstream/mjpegstreamdlg_views.cpp:80
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"The %1 server allows to share items through the local network using a web "
"browser. Motion JPEG is a video compression format in which each video frame "
"is compressed separately as a JPEG image. MJPEG stream is a standard which "
"allows network clients to be connected without additional module. Most major "
"web browsers and players support MJPEG stream. To access the stream from "
"your browser, just use http://address:port as url, with address the MJPEG "
"server IP, and port the server port set in this config dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ceadaíonn an freastalaí %1 míreanna a roinnt tríd an líonra áitiúil ag baint "
"úsáide as brabhsálaí gréasáin. Is formáid comhbhrú físe é Motion JPEG ina "
"ndéantar gach fráma físe a chomhbhrú ar leithligh mar íomhá JPEG. Is "
"caighdeán é sruth MJPEG a ligeann do chliaint líonra a bheith ceangailte gan "
"modúl breise. Tacaíonn formhór na mbrabhsálaithe gréasáin agus na "
"seinnteoirí móra le sruth MJPEG. Chun rochtain a fháil ar an sruth ó do "
"bhrabhsálaí, bain úsáid as http://address:port mar url, leis an seoladh IP "
"freastalaí MJPEG, agus port an port freastalaí atá socraithe sa dialóg "
"chumraíochta seo."

