#, kde-format
msgid "MJPEG Stream Server"
msgstr "Freastalaí Srutha MJPEG"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/mjpegstream/mjpegstreamplugin.cpp:68
#, kde-format
msgid "A tool to export items as MJPEG Stream"
msgstr "Uirlis chun míreanna a easpórtáil mar shruth MJPEG"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/mjpegstream/mjpegstreamplugin.cpp:84
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>This tool allows users to share items on the local network through a "
"MJPEG Stream server.</p><p>Items to share can be selected one by one or by "
"group through a selection of albums.</p><p>Motion JPEG is a video "
"compression format in which each video frame or interlaced field of a "
"digital video sequence is compressed separately as a JPEG image. MJPEG "
"stream is a standard which allows network clients to be connected without "
"additional module. Most major web browsers and players support MJPEG stream."
"</p><p>To access the stream from your browser, use http://address:port as "
"url, with address the MJPEG address, and port the MJPEG port set in config "
"dialog. More than one computer can be connected to the MJPEG server at the "
"same time.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Ligeann an uirlis seo d'úsáideoirí míreanna a roinnt ar an líonra áitiúil "
"trí fhreastalaí Sruth MJPEG.</p><p>Is féidir míreanna le roinnt a roghnú "
"ceann ar cheann nó de réir grúpa trí rogha albam.</p><p>Is formáid comhbhrú "
"físe é Motion JPEG ina ndéantar gach fráma físe nó réimse fite fuaite de "
"sheicheamh físe digiteach a chomhbhrú ar leithligh mar íomhá JPEG. Is "
"caighdeán é sruth MJPEG a ligeann do chliaint líonra a bheith ceangailte gan "
"modúl breise. Tacaíonn formhór na mbrabhsálaithe gréasáin agus na "
"seinnteoirí móra le sruth MJPEG.</p><p>Chun rochtain a fháil ar an sruth ó "
"do bhrabhsálaí, bain úsáid as http://address:port mar url, leis an seoladh "
"MJPEG ag an seoladh address, agus an port MJPEG atá socraithe sa dialóg "
"chumraíochta. Is féidir níos mó ná ríomhaire amháin a bheith ceangailte leis "
"an bhfreastalaí MJPEG ag an am céanna.</p>"

