#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/panoramaplugin.cpp:67
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>This tool allows users to assemble images together to create large "
"panorama.</p><p>To create panorama image, you need to use images taken from "
"same point of view with a tripod and exposed with same settings.</p><p>The "
"tool is able to assemble shots taken horizontally, vertically, or as a "
"matrix. Take care that target image will become huge and require a lot of "
"memory to be processed.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Ligeann an uirlis seo d’úsáideoirí íomhánna a chur le chéile chun radharc "
"mór lánléargais a chruthú.</p><p>Chun íomhá lánléargais a chruthú, ní mór "
"duit íomhánna a tógadh ón dearcadh céanna le tríphos agus nochta leis na "
"socruithe céanna a úsáid.</p><p>Is féidir leis an uirlis íomhánna a tógadh "
"go cothrománach, go hingearach, nó mar mhaitrís a chur le chéile. Bí "
"cúramach go mbeidh an íomhá sprice ollmhór agus go mbeidh go leor cuimhne ag "
"teastáil le próiseáil.</p>"

