#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:92
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Name of the panorama file (without its extension)."
msgstr "Ainm an chomhaid lánléargais (gan a shíneadh)."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:93
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"File name template\": Set here the base name of the files that will be "
"saved. For example, if your template is \"panorama\" and if you chose a JPEG "
"output, then your panorama will be saved with the name \"panorama.jpg\". If "
"you choose to save also the project file, it will have the name \"panorama."
"pto\"."
msgstr ""
"\"Teimpléad ainm comhaid\": Socraigh anseo bunainm na gcomhad a shábhálfar. "
"Mar shampla, más é \"panorama\" do theimpléad agus má roghnaigh tú aschur "
"JPEG, sábhálfar do phanorama faoin ainm \"panorama.jpg\". Má roghnaíonn tú "
"an comhad tionscadail a shábháil freisin, beidh an t-ainm \"panorama.pto\" "
"air."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:100
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Save project file"
msgstr "Sábháil comhad tionscadail"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:102
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Save the project file for further processing within Hugin GUI."
msgstr ""
"Sábháil an comhad tionscadail le haghaidh tuilleadh próiseála laistigh de "
"Chomhéadan Grafach Hugin."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:103
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"Save project file\": You can keep the project file generated to stitch "
"your panorama for further tweaking within %1 by checking this. This is "
"useful if you want a different projection, modify the horizon or the center "
"of the panorama, or modify the control points to get better results."
msgstr ""
"\"Sábháil comhad tionscadail\": Is féidir leat an comhad tionscadail a "
"ghintear chun do lánléargas a shníomh a choinneáil le haghaidh tuilleadh "
"feabhsúcháin laistigh de %1 tríd an rogha seo a sheiceáil. Tá sé seo "
"úsáideach más mian leat teilgean difriúil, an léaslíne nó lár an lánléargais "
"a mhodhnú, nó na pointí rialaithe a mhodhnú chun torthaí níos fearr a fháil."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:208
#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:217
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title: dialog"
msgid "Warning"
msgstr "Rabhadh"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:209
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "This file already exists"
msgstr "Tá an comhad seo ann cheana féin"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:218
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid ""
"One or more converted raw files already exists (they will be skipped during "
"the copying process)"
msgstr ""
"Tá comhad amha tiontaithe amháin nó níos mó ann cheana féin (déanfar iad a "
"scipeáil le linn an phróisis chóipeála)"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:263
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Panorama Stitching is Done"
msgstr "Tá Fuáil Panorama Críochnaithe"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:264
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Congratulations. Your images are stitched into a panorama."
msgstr "Comhghairdeas. Tá do chuid íomhánna fuaite i bpríomhghraf lánléargais."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:265
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Your panorama will be created to the directory:"
msgstr "Cruthófar do lánléargas chuig an eolaire:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:267
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "once you press the \"Finish\" button, with the name set below."
msgstr ""
"nuair a bhrúnn tú an cnaipe \"Críochnaigh\", leis an ainm socraithe thíos."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:268
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"If you choose to save the project file, and if your images were raw images "
"then the converted images used during the stitching process will be copied "
"at the same time (those are TIFF files that can be big)."
msgstr ""
"Má roghnaíonn tú an comhad tionscadail a shábháil, agus má bhí d’íomhánna "
"amha, déanfar na híomhánna tiontaithe a úsáideadh le linn an phróisis fuála "
"a chóipeáil ag an am céanna (is comhaid TIFF iad sin a d’fhéadfadh a bheith "
"mór)."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panolastpage.cpp:297
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Error"
msgstr "Earráid"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:83
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title: window"
msgid "Optimization"
msgstr "Uasmhéadú"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:97
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option: check"
msgid "Level horizon"
msgstr "Léaslíne cothrom"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: tooltip"
msgid "Detect the horizon and adapt the project to make it horizontal."
msgstr ""
"Braith an léaslíne agus oiriúnaigh an tionscadal chun é a dhéanamh "
"cothrománach."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:100
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"Level horizon\": Detect the horizon and adapt the projection so that the "
"detected horizon is an horizontal line in the final panorama"
msgstr ""
"\"Líne chothrom\": Braith an léaslíne agus oiriúnaigh an teilgean ionas go "
"mbeidh an léaslíne braite ina líne chothrománach sa lánléargas deiridh"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:171
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Optimization is in progress, please wait."
msgstr "Tá an t-optamú ar siúl, fan le do thoil."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:205
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"The optimization step according to your settings is ready to be performed."
msgstr "Tá an chéim optamaithe de réir do shocruithe réidh le déanamh."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:206
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"This step can include an automatic leveling of the horizon, and also an "
"automatic projection selection and size."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leis an gcéim seo leibhéalú uathoibríoch na spéire a áireamh, agus "
"roghnú agus méid teilgean uathoibríoch freisin."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:208
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "To perform this operation, the \"%1\" program will be used."
msgstr "Chun an oibríocht seo a dhéanamh, úsáidfear an clár \"%1\"."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:210
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Press the \"Next\" button to run the optimization."
msgstr "Brúigh an cnaipe \"Ar Aghaidh\" chun an t-optamú a rith."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panooptimizepage.cpp:310
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Optimization has failed."
msgstr "Theip ar an optamú."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:85
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title: window"
msgid "Pre-Processing Images"
msgstr "Réamhphróiseáil Íomhánna"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option: check"
msgid "Detect moving skies"
msgstr "Braith spéartha gluaiseachta"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:101
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: tooltip"
msgid ""
"Automatic detection of clouds to prevent wrong keypoints matching between "
"images due to moving clouds."
msgstr ""
"Brath uathoibríoch scamall chun cosc a chur ar mheaitseáil mhícheart ar "
"phointí eochair idir íomhánna mar gheall ar scamaill ag gluaiseacht."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:103
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: whatsthis"
msgid ""
"\"Detect moving skies\": During the control points selection and matching, "
"this option discards any points that are associated to a possible cloud. "
"This is useful to prevent moving clouds from altering the control points "
"matching process."
msgstr ""
"\"Braith spéartha gluaisteacha\": Le linn roghnú agus meaitseáil pointí "
"rialaithe, caitheann an rogha seo aon phointí a bhaineann le scamall "
"féideartha ar leataobh. Tá sé seo úsáideach chun cosc a chur ar scamaill "
"ghluaisteacha an próiseas meaitseála pointí rialaithe a athrú."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:188
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Now, we will pre-process images before stitching them."
msgstr ""
"Anois, déanfaimid réamhphróiseáil ar íomhánna sula ndéanfaimid iad a fhuáil."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/panorama/wizard/panopreprocesspage.cpp:191
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Pre-processing also includes a calculation of some control points to match "
"overlaps between images. For that purpose, the \"%1\" program will be used."
msgstr ""
"Áirítear leis an réamhphróiseáil ríomh roinnt pointí rialaithe chun forluí "
"idir íomhánna a mheaitseáil. Chun na críche sin, úsáidfear an clár \"%1\"."

