#, kde-format
msgid "Equalization Strength:"
msgstr "Neart Cothromúcháin:"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/videoslideshow/vidslideoutputpage.cpp:178
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This controls strength of equalization. Setting this option to zero "
"effectively does nothing."
msgstr ""
"Rialaíonn sé seo neart an chothromúcháin. Ní dhéanann sé tada ar chor ar "
"bith má shocraítear an rogha seo go náid."

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/videoslideshow/vidslideoutputpage.cpp:183
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<i>These settings apply temporal midway video equalization effect while "
"encoding frames as video. This adjusts the sequence of frames to have the "
"same histograms, while maintaining their dynamics as much as possible. It’s "
"useful for e.g. matching exposures from a timelapse sequence.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Cuireann na socruithe seo éifeacht chothromúcháin físe leathbhealaigh ama "
"i bhfeidhm agus frámaí á n-ionchódú mar fhíseán. Coigeartaíonn sé seo "
"seicheamh na bhfrámaí chun na histeagraim chéanna a bheith acu, agus a "
"ndinimic á coinneáil a oiread agus is féidir. Tá sé úsáideach, mar shampla, "
"chun nochtadh ó sheicheamh luasghéaraithe ama a mheaitseáil.</i>"

#: core/dplugins/generic/tools/videoslideshow/vidslideoutputpage.cpp:195
#, kde-format
