#: core/dplugins/generic/view/slideshow/slideshowplugin.cpp:70
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>This tool render a series of items as a simple slide-show.</p><p>Plenty "
"of items properties can be displayed as overlay while running.</p><p>This "
"tool can play album contents in recursive mode with children albums if any.</"
"p><p><u>Usage:</u></p><table><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><nobr><center><b><h1>Item "
"Access</h1></b></center></nobr></td></tr><tr><td>Previous Item:</"
"td><td><i>Up</i> key</td></tr><tr><td></td><td><i>PgUp</i> key</td></"
"tr><tr><td></td><td><i>Left</i> key</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Mouse wheel "
"up</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Left mouse button</td></tr><tr><td>Next Item:</"
"td><td><i>Down</i> key</td></tr><tr><td></td><td><i>PgDown</i> key</td></"
"tr><tr><td></td><td><i>Right</i> key</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Mouse wheel "
"down</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Right mouse button</td></tr><tr><td>Pause/"
"Start:</td><td><i>Space</i> key</td></tr><tr><td>Video forward:</"
"td><td><i>Ctrl+Right</i> key</td></tr><tr><td>Video backward:</td><td><i>Ctrl"
"+Left</i> key</td></tr><tr><td>Slideshow Settings:</td><td><i>Alt+P</i> key</"
"td></tr><tr><td>Hide/Show Overlays:</td><td><i>Alt+Y</i> key</td></"
"tr><tr><td>Quit:</td><td><i>Esc</i> key</td></tr><tr><td colspan="
"\"2\"><nobr><center><b><h1>Item Properties</h1></b></center></nobr></td></"
"tr><tr><td>Change Tags:</td><td>Use Tags keyboard shortcuts</td></"
"tr><tr><td>Change Rating:</td><td>Use Rating keyboard shortcuts</td></"
"tr><tr><td>Change Color Label:</td><td>Use Color label keyboard shortcuts</"
"td></tr><tr><td>Change Pick Label:</td><td>Use Pick label keyboard "
"shortcuts</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><nobr><center><b><h1>Others</h1></"
"b></center></nobr></td></tr><tr><td>Show this help:</td><td><i>F1</i> key</"
"td></tr></table>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Déanann an uirlis seo sraith míreanna a léiriú mar shleamhnán simplí.</"
"p><p>Is féidir neart airíonna míreanna a thaispeáint mar fhorleagan agus í "
"ag rith.</p><p>Is féidir leis an uirlis seo ábhar albam a sheinm i mód "
"athchúrsach le halbaim leanaí más ann dóibh.</p><p><u>Úsáid:</u></"
"p><table><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><nobr><center><b><h1>Rochtain ar Mhíreanna</"
"h1></b></center></nobr></td></tr><tr><td>Mír Roimhe Seo:</td><td><i>Eochair "
"Suas</i></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><i>Eochair Leathanach Suas</i></td></"
"tr><tr><td></td><td><i>Eochair Chlé</i></td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Roth na "
"luiche suas</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Luch chlé cnaipe</td></tr><tr><td>An "
"Chéad Mhír Eile:</td><td><i>Eochair Síos</i></td></tr><tr><td></"
"td><td><i>Eochair Leathanach Síos</i></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><i>Eochair "
"Deas</i></td></tr><tr><td></td><td>Roth na luiche síos</td></tr><tr><td></"
"td><td>Cnaipe deas na luiche</td></tr><tr><td>Sos/Tosaigh:</"
"td><td><i>Eochair Spáis</i></td></tr><tr><td>Físeán ar aghaidh:</"
"td><td><i>Ctrl+Eochair Dheas</i></td></tr><tr><td>Físeán ar ais:</"
"td><td><i>Ctrl+Eochair Chlé</i></td></tr><tr><td>Taispeántas Sleamhnán "
"Socruithe:</td><td><i>Alt+P</i></td></tr><tr><td>Folaigh/Taispeáin Forleagan:"
"</td><td><i>Alt+Y</i></td></tr><tr><td>Scoir:</td><td><i>Eochair Esc</i></"
"td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><nobr><center><b><h1>Airíonna Míre</h1></b></"
"center></nobr></td></tr><tr><td>Athraigh Clibeanna:</td><td>Úsáid aicearraí "
"méarchláir Clibeanna</td></tr><tr><td>Athraigh Rátáil:</td><td>Úsáid "
"aicearraí méarchláir Rátála</td></tr><tr><td>Athraigh Lipéad Datha:</"
"td><td>Úsáid aicearraí méarchláir Lipéad Datha</td></tr><tr><td>Athraigh "
"Lipéad Roghnaithe:</td><td>Úsáid aicearraí méarchláir Lipéad Roghnaithe</"
"td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><nobr><center><b><h1>Eile</h1></b></center></"
"nobr></td></tr><tr><td>Taispeáin an chabhair seo:</td><td><i>Eochair F1</i></"
"td></tr></table>"

