#: core/libs/album/manager/albummanager_database.cpp:266
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Your database character set has changed since this album was last opened.\n"
"Old character set: %1, new character set: %2\n"
"If you have recently changed your database character set, you need not be "
"concerned.\n"
"Please note that if you switched to a database character set that does not "
"support some of the filenames in your collection, these files may no longer "
"be found in the collection. If you are sure that you want to continue, click "
"'Yes'. Otherwise, click 'No' and correct your database character set setting "
"before restarting digiKam."
msgstr ""
"Tá athrú tagtha ar do shraith carachtar bunachar sonraí ó osclaíodh an t-"
"albam seo go deireanach.\n"
"Sean-shraith carachtar: %1, sraith carachtar nua: %2\n"
"Mura n-athraigh tú do shraith carachtar bunachar sonraí le déanaí, ní gá "
"duit a bheith buartha.\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara, le do thoil, má d'athraigh tú go sraith carachtar "
"bunachar sonraí nach dtacaíonn le cuid de na hainmneacha comhad i do "
"bhailiúchán, go mb'fhéidir nach mbeidh na comhaid seo le fáil sa bhailiúchán "
"a thuilleadh. Má tá tú cinnte gur mian leat leanúint ar aghaidh, cliceáil "
"'Tá'. Seachas sin, cliceáil 'Níl' agus ceartaigh socrú do shraith carachtar "
"bunachar sonraí sula n-atosóidh tú digiKam."

