msgstr "Tá bailiúchán ann cheana féin ina bhfuil an fillteán \"%1\""

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:284
#, kde-format
msgid "The storage media can be uniquely identified."
msgstr "Is féidir na meáin stórála a aithint go huathúil."

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:296
#, kde-format
msgid "The collection is located on your harddisk"
msgstr "Tá an bailiúchán suite ar do dhiosca crua"

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:336
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This is a CD/DVD, which is identified by the label that you can set in your "
"CD burning application. There is already another entry with the same label. "
"The two will be distinguished by the files in the top directory, so please "
"do not append files to the CD, or it will not be recognized. In the future, "
"please set a unique label on your CDs and DVDs if you intend to use them "
"with digiKam."
msgstr ""
"Is CD/DVD é seo, a aithnítear leis an lipéad is féidir leat a shocrú i "
"d'fheidhmchlár dóite CD. Tá iontráil eile ann cheana féin leis an lipéad "
"céanna. Déanfar idirdhealú idir an dá cheann de réir na gcomhad san eolaire "
"uachtarach, mar sin ná cuir comhaid leis an CD, nó ní aithneofar é. Amach "
"anseo, socraigh lipéad uathúil ar do CDanna agus DVDanna má tá sé ar intinn "
"agat iad a úsáid le digiKam."

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:351
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This is a CD/DVD. It will be identified by the label (\"%1\")that you have "
"set in your CD burning application. If you create further CDs for use with "
"digikam in the future, please remember to give them a unique label as well."
msgstr ""
"Is CD/DVD é seo. Aithneofar é leis an lipéad (\"%1\") atá socraithe agat i "
"d'fheidhmchlár dóite CD. Má chruthaíonn tú CDanna eile le húsáid le digikam "
"amach anseo, cuimhnigh lipéad uathúil a thabhairt dóibh chomh maith."

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:367
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This is a removable storage medium that will be identified by its label "
"(\"%1\")"
msgstr "Meán stórála inbhainte é seo a aithneofar lena lipéad (\"%1\")"

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:383
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This entry will only be identified by the path where it is found on your "
"system (\"%1\"). No more specific means of identification (UUID, label) is "
"available."
msgstr ""
"Ní aithneofar an iontráil seo ach amháin tríd an gcosán ina bhfuil sí le "
"fáil ar do chóras (\"%1\"). Níl aon mhodh aitheantais níos sainiúla (UUID, "
"lipéad) ar fáil."

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:400
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"It is not possible on your system to identify the storage medium of this "
"path. It will be added using the file path as the only identifier. This will "
"work well for your local hard disk."
msgstr ""
"Ní féidir ar do chóras meán stórála an chosáin seo a aithint. Cuirfear leis "
"é ag baint úsáide as an gcosán comhaid mar an t-aon aitheantóir. Oibreoidh "
"sé seo go maith le haghaidh do dhiosca crua áitiúil."

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:425
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You need to locally mount your Samba share. Sorry, digiKam does currently "
"not support smb:// URLs. "
msgstr ""
"Ní mór duit do chomhroinnt Samba a fheistiú go háitiúil. Tá brón orainn, ní "
"thacaíonn digiKam le URLanna smb:// faoi láthair. "

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:430
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Your network storage must be set up to be accessible as files and folders "
"through the operating system. digiKam does not support remote URLs."
msgstr ""
"Ní mór do stóras líonra a bheith socraithe le bheith inrochtana mar chomhaid "
"agus fillteáin tríd an gcóras oibriúcháin. Ní thacaíonn digiKam le URLanna "
"iargúlta."

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:467
#, kde-format
msgid "There is already a collection for a network share with the same path."
msgstr ""
"Tá bailiúchán ann cheana féin le haghaidh comhroinnt líonra leis an gcosán "
"céanna."

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_location.cpp:480
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The network share will be identified by the path you selected. If the path "
"is empty, the share will be considered unavailable."
msgstr ""
"Aithneofar an sciar líonra de réir an chosáin a roghnaigh tú. Mura bhfuil an "
"cosán ar fáil, measfar nach bhfuil an sciar ar fáil."

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_p.cpp:475
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"\"relative path\" on harddisk partition with \"UUID\"\n"
"Folder \"%1\" on the volume with the id \"%2\""
msgstr ""
"\"cosán coibhneasta\" ar dheighilt dhiosca crua le \"UUID\"\n"
"Fillteán \"%1\" ar an toirt leis an aitheantas \"%2\""

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_p.cpp:483
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"\"relative path\" on harddisk partition with \"label\"\n"
"Folder \"%1\" on the volume labeled \"%2\""
msgstr ""
"\"cosán coibhneasta\" ar dheighilt dhiosca crua le \"lipéad\"\n"
"Fillteán \"%1\" ar an toirt lipéadaithe \"%2\""

#: core/libs/database/collection/collectionmanager_p.cpp:497
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Shared directory mounted at \"%1\""
msgstr "Eolaire comhroinnte suite ag \"%1\""

