#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:72
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Select here the type of database backend.</p><p><b>SQlite</b> backend is "
"for local database storage with a small or medium collection sizes. It is "
"the default and recommended backend for collections with less than 100K "
"items.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Roghnaigh anseo an cineál cúltaca bunachar sonraí.</p><p><b>SQlite</b>Is "
"le haghaidh stórála bunachar sonraí áitiúil le méideanna beaga nó meánacha "
"atá cúltaca SQlite. Is é an cúltaca réamhshocraithe agus molta é do "
"bhailiúcháin a bhfuil níos lú ná 100K mír iontu.</p>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:81
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p><b>MySQL Internal</b> backend is for local database storage with huge "
"collection sizes. This backend is recommend for local collections with more "
"than 100K items.</p>"
msgstr ""
"Is le haghaidh stórála bunachar sonraí áitiúil le méideanna ollmhóra "
"bailiúcháin atá an chúltaca <p><b>MySQL Internal</b>. Moltar an chúltaca seo "
"do bhailiúcháin áitiúla le níos mó ná 100K mír.</p>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:86
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p><b>MySQL Server</b> backend is a more robust solution especially for "
"remote and shared database storage. It is also more efficient to manage huge "
"collection sizes with more than 100K items.</p>"
msgstr ""
"Is réiteach níos láidre é cúltaca <p><b>MySQL Server</b> go háirithe le "
"haghaidh stórála bunachar sonraí iargúlta agus comhroinnte. Tá sé níos "
"éifeachtaí freisin chun méideanna ollmhóra bailiúcháin a bhainistiú le níos "
"mó ná 100K mír.</p>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:93
#, kde-format
