msgstr "Faigh eolas faoi <b>Chineál Bunachar Sonraí</b>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:107
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:database path"
msgid "Path: "
msgstr "Cosán: "

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:115
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Get information about <b>Database Path</b>"
msgstr "Faigh eolas faoi <b>Chonair Bunachar Sonraí</b>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:117
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"<p>Set here the location where the database files will be stored on your "
"system. There are four databases: one for all collections properties, one to "
"store compressed thumbnails, one to store faces recognition metadata, and "
"one to store similarity fingerprints.<br>Write access is required to be able "
"to edit image properties.</p><p>Databases are digiKam core engines. Take "
"care to use a place hosted by fast hardware (eg. SSD or NVMe) with enough "
"free space especially for thumbnails database.</p><p>Note: a remote file "
"system such as NFS, cannot be used here. For performance reasons, it is also "
"recommended not to use network storage media.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Socraigh anseo an suíomh ina stórálfar comhaid an bhunachair shonraí ar "
"do chóras. Tá ceithre bhunachar sonraí ann: ceann amháin do gach airíonna "
"bailiúcháin, ceann amháin chun mionsamhlacha comhbhrúite a stóráil, ceann "
"amháin chun meiteashonraí aitheantais aghaidheanna a stóráil, agus ceann "
"amháin chun méarloirg chosúlachta a stóráil.<br>Tá rochtain "
"scríbhneoireachta ag teastáil chun airíonna íomhá a chur in eagar.</p><p>Is "
"innill lárnacha digiKam iad bunachair shonraí. Bí cúramach áit a úsáid atá á "
"óstáil ag crua-earraí tapa (m.sh. SSD nó NVMe) le dóthain spáis saor go "
"háirithe do bhunachar sonraí mionsamhlacha.</p><p>Tabhair faoi deara: ní "
"féidir córas comhad iargúlta ar nós NFS a úsáid anseo. Ar chúiseanna "
"feidhmíochta, moltar gan meáin stórála líonra a úsáid freisin.</p>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:141
#, kde-format
msgid "Enable WAL mode for the databases"
msgstr "Cumasaigh mód WAL do na bunachair shonraí"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:142
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The WAL (Write-Ahead Log) mode is significantly faster in most scenarios on "
"supported systems."
msgstr ""
"Tá an modh WAL (Log Scríofa Roimh Ré) i bhfad níos tapúla i bhformhór na "
"gcásanna ar chórais a dtacaítear leo."

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:149
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Get information about <b>WAL Mode</b>"
msgstr "Faigh eolas faoi <b>Mód WAL</b>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:150
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Write-Ahead Log is a mode to use a roll-forward journal that records "
"transactions that have been committed but not yet applied to the databases. "
"It uses an auxiliary journalized file to host structures for recovery "
"transactions during a crash. The changes are first recorded in the log, "
"before the changes are written to the database. This made database requests "
"atomic and robust in extensive and critical use cases."
msgstr ""
"Is modh é Log Scríofa Roimh Ré chun dialann rollta ar aghaidh a úsáid a "
"thaifeadann idirbhearta atá tiomanta ach nár cuireadh i bhfeidhm ar na "
"bunachair shonraí go fóill. Úsáideann sé comhad cúnta dialainne chun "
"struchtúir a óstáil le haghaidh idirbhearta aisghabhála le linn tuairteála. "
"Déantar na hathruithe a thaifeadadh sa log ar dtús, sula scríobhtar na "
"hathruithe chuig an mbunachar sonraí. Rinne sé seo iarratais bunachar sonraí "
"adamhach agus láidir i gcásanna úsáide fairsinge agus criticiúla."

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:169
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Here you can configure locations where MySQL binary tools are located. "
"digiKam will try to find these binaries automatically if they are already "
"installed on your computer.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Anseo is féidir leat suíomhanna a chumrú ina bhfuil uirlisí dénártha "
"MySQL suite. Déanfaidh digiKam iarracht na comhaid dénártha seo a aimsiú go "
"huathoibríoch má tá siad suiteáilte ar do ríomhaire cheana féin.</p>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:178
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:group"
