#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:326
#, kde-format
msgid "Database Server Instructions"
msgstr "Treoracha Freastalaí Bunachar Sonraí"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:328
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>digiKam expects that database is already created with a dedicated user "
"account. This user name <i>digikam</i> will require full access to the "
"database.<br>If your database is not already set up, you can use the "
"following SQL commands (after replacing the <b><i>password</i></b> with the "
"correct one).</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Tá súil ag digiKam go bhfuil an bunachar sonraí sin cruthaithe cheana "
"féin le cuntas úsáideora tiomnaithe. Beidh rochtain iomlán ar an mbunachar "
"sonraí ag teastáil don ainm úsáideora <i>digikam</i> seo.<br>Mura bhfuil do "
"bhunachar sonraí socraithe cheana féin, is féidir leat na horduithe SQL seo "
"a leanas a úsáid (tar éis an <b><i>pasfhocal</i></b> a athsholáthar leis an "
"gceann ceart).</p>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:341
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Note: with a Linux server, a database can be initialized following the "
"commands below:</p><p># su</p><p># systemctl restart mysqld</p><p># mysql -u "
"root</p><p>...</p><p>Enter SQL code to Mysql prompt in order to init digiKam "
"databases with grant privileges (see behind)</p><p>...</p><p>quit</"
"p><p>NOTE: If you have problems with a MySQL server on Ubuntu based Linux "
"system, use the addition command in the mysql prompt to be able to create "
"MySQL triggers.<br>SET GLOBAL log_bin_trust_function_creators=1;</p><p>NOTE: "
"If you have an enormous collection, you should start MySQL server with mysql "
"--max_allowed_packet=128M OR in my.ini or ~/.my.cnf, change the settings</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Nóta: le freastalaí Linux, is féidir bunachar sonraí a thosú trí na "
"horduithe seo a leanas a leanúint:</p><p># su</p><p># systemctl restart "
"mysqld</p><p># mysql -u root</p><p>...</p><p>Cuir isteach cód SQL sa leid "
"Mysql chun bunachair shonraí digiKam a thosú le pribhléidí deonaithe (féach "
"taobh thiar)</p><p>...</p><p>quit</p><p>NÓTA: Má bhíonn fadhbanna agat le "
"freastalaí MySQL ar chóras Linux bunaithe ar Ubuntu, bain úsáid as an ordú "
"breise sa leid mysql chun go mbeidh tú in ann spreagthóirí MySQL a chruthú."
"<br>SET GLOBAL log_bin_trust_function_creators=1;</p><p>NÓTA: Má tá "
"bailiúchán ollmhór agat, ba chóir duit freastalaí MySQL a thosú le mysql --"
"max_allowed_packet=128M NÓ i my.ini nó ~/.my.cnf, athraigh na socruithe</p>"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:365
#, kde-format
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Riachtanais"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:369
#, kde-format
msgid "Database Server Technical Details"
msgstr "Sonraí Teicniúla Freastalaí Bunachar Sonraí"

#: core/libs/database/utils/widgets/dbsettingswidget.cpp:371
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Use this configuration view to set all information to be connected to a "
"remote <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MySQL\">Mysql database "
"server</a> (or <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MariaDB\">MariaDB</"
"a>) through a network. As with Sqlite or MySQL internal server, 3 databases "
"will be stored on the remote server: one for all collections properties, one "
"to store compressed thumbnails, and one to store faces recognition metadata."
"</p><p>Unlike Sqlite or MySQL internal server, you can customize the "
"database names to simplify your backups.</p><p>Databases are digiKam core "
"engines. To prevent performance issues, take a care to use a fast network "
"link between the client and the server computers. It is also recommended to "
"host database files on fast hardware (as <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Solid-state_drive\">SSD</a>) with enough free space, especially for "
"thumbnails database, even if data are compressed using wavelets image format "
"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Progressive_Graphics_File\">PGF</a>."
"</p><p>The databases must be created previously on the remote server by the "
"administrator. Look in <b>Requirements</b> tab for details.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Úsáid an radharc cumraíochta seo chun an fhaisnéis go léir a shocrú le "
"ceangal le freastalaí <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MySQL"
"\">bunachair shonraí Mysql</a> cianda (nó <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/MariaDB\">MariaDB</a>) trí líonra. Mar atá le freastalaí inmheánach "
"Sqlite nó MySQL, stórálfar 3 bhunachar sonraí ar an bhfreastalaí cianda: "
"ceann amháin do gach airí bailiúcháin, ceann amháin chun mionsamhlacha "
"comhbhrúite a stóráil, agus ceann amháin chun meiteashonraí aitheantais "
"aghaidheanna a stóráil.</p><p>Murab ionann agus freastalaí inmheánach Sqlite "
"nó MySQL, is féidir leat ainmneacha na mbunachar sonraí a shaincheapadh chun "
"do chúltacaí a shimpliú.</p><p>Is innill lárnacha digiKam iad bunachair "
"shonraí. Chun fadhbanna feidhmíochta a chosc, bí cúramach nasc líonra tapa a "
"úsáid idir an cliant agus ríomhairí an fhreastalaí. Moltar freisin comhaid "
"bhunachar sonraí a óstáil ar chrua-earraí gasta (mar <a href=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Solid-state_drive\">SSD</a>) le dóthain spáis saor, go "
"háirithe do bhunachar sonraí mionsamhlacha, fiú má tá na sonraí comhbhrúite "
"ag baint úsáide as formáid íomhá tonnta <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Progressive_Graphics_File\">PGF</a>.</p><p>Ní mór don riarthóir na "
"bunachair shonraí a chruthú roimhe seo ar an bhfreastalaí cianda. Féach sa "
"chluaisín <b>Riachtanais</b> le haghaidh sonraí.</p>"

