#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingfilter.cpp:58
#, kde-format
msgid "Anti-Vignetting Tool"
msgstr "Uirlis Frith-Vignetting"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:82
#, kde-format
msgid "Add vignetting"
msgstr "Cuir vignetting leis"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:83
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This option adds vignetting to the image instead of removing it. Use it for "
"creative effects."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an rogha seo vignetting leis an íomhá in ionad é a bhaint. Bain "
"úsáid as le haghaidh éifeachtaí cruthaitheacha."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:92
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You can see here a thumbnail preview of the anti-vignetting mask applied to "
"the image."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat réamhamharc mionsamhail den masc frith-vignetting a cuireadh "
"i bhfeidhm ar an íomhá a fheiceáil anseo."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:97
#: core/libs/dimg/filters/sharp/sharpsettings.cpp:169
#, kde-format
msgid "Amount:"
msgstr "Cainníocht:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:102
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This value controls the degree of intensity of the filter at its point of "
"maximum density."
msgstr "Rialaíonn an luach seo déine an scagaire ag a phointe uasdlúis."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:107
#, kde-format
msgid "Feather:"
msgstr "Cleite:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:112
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This value is used as the exponent controlling the fall-off in density from "
"the inner circle of the filter to the outer circle."
msgstr ""
"Úsáidtear an luach seo mar an easpónant a rialaíonn an titim i dlús ón "
"gciorcal istigh den scagaire go dtí an ciorcal seachtrach."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:118
#, kde-format
msgid "Inner Radius:"
msgstr "Ga Inmheánach:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:123
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This value is the radius of the inner circle of the filter. In the inner "
"circle the image is preserved. It is expressed as a multiple of the outer "
"radius of the filter."
msgstr ""
"Is é an luach seo ga an chiorcail istigh den scagaire. Sa chiorcal istigh, "
"caomhnaítear an íomhá. Léirítear é mar iolraí de gha seachtrach an scagaire."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:129
#, kde-format
msgid "Outer Radius:"
msgstr "Ga Seachtrach:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:134
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This value is the radius of the outer circle of the filter. Outside the "
"outer circle the effect of the filter is at its maximum. It is expressed as "
"a multiple of the diagonal of the image."
msgstr ""
"Is é an luach seo ga an chiorcail sheachtraigh den scagaire. Lasmuigh den "
"chiorcal seachtrach bíonn éifeacht an scagaire ag a uasmhéid. Léirítear é "
"mar iolraí de thrasnán na híomhá."

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:140
#, kde-format
msgid "X offset:"
msgstr "Fritháireamh X:"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:145
#, kde-format
msgid "X offset "
msgstr "Fritháireamh X "

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/lens/antivignettingsettings.cpp:149
