#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:105
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label short translated text about the Face Workflow."
msgid "Workflow:"
msgstr "Sreabhadh oibre:"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:109
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:listbox"
msgid "Scan new images"
msgstr "Scanáil íomhánna nua"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:110
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:listbox"
msgid "Scan all images"
msgstr "Scanáil na híomhánna go léir"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:111
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:listbox"
msgid "Recognize faces only"
msgstr "Aithint aghaidheanna amháin"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:113
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"digiKam can search for faces in your photos.<br>When you have identified "
"your friends on a number of photos,<br>it can also recognize the people "
"shown on your photos.<p><b>Scan new images</b> will scan for faces and "
"attempt recognition for new images found in the albums selected in the "
"\"Search in\" tab.</p><p><b>Scan all images</b> will scan for faces and "
"attempt recognition for all images found in the albums selected in the "
"\"Search in\" tab.</p><p><b>Recognize faces only</b> will try to match "
"unknown faces with confirmed faces without scanning images new faces.</p>"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le digiKam aghaidheanna a chuardach i do ghrianghraif.<br>Nuair a "
"bheidh do chairde aitheanta agat ar roinnt grianghraf,<br>is féidir leis na "
"daoine a thaispeántar ar do ghrianghraif a aithint freisin. Déanfaidh "
"<p><b>Scanadh íomhánna nua</b> scanadh ar aghaidheanna agus iarracht "
"íomhánna nua a aimsítear sna halbaim a roghnaíodh sa chluaisín \"Cuardaigh i"
"\" a aithint.</p><p><b>Scanadh gach íomhá</b> scanadh ar aghaidheanna agus "
"iarracht íomhánna uile a aimsítear sna halbaim a roghnaíodh sa chluaisín "
"\"Cuardaigh i\" a aithint.</p><p><b>Aithint aghaidheanna amháin</b> "
"déanfaidh sé iarracht aghaidheanna anaithnide a mheaitseáil le haghaidheanna "
"deimhnithe gan íomhánna aghaidheanna nua a scanadh.</p>"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:131
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label short translated text about the Face Detection Accuracy"
msgid "Accuracy:"
msgstr "Cruinneas:"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:138
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Adjust sensitivity versus specificity: the higher the value, the more "
"accurately faces will<br>be detected, but less faces will be detected."
msgstr ""
"Coigeartaigh íogaireacht i gcoinne sainiúlachta: dá airde an luach, is ea is "
"cruinne a bhraitear aghaidheanna, ach braitear níos lú aghaidheanna."

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:143
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label with a short translated text about the face size for detection"
msgid "Face size:"
msgstr "Méid aghaidhe:"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:147
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label: listbox face size"
msgid "Extra Small"
msgstr "An-bheag"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:148
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label: listbox face size"
msgid "Small"
msgstr "Beag"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:149
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label: listbox face size"
msgid "Medium"
msgstr "Meánach"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:150
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label: listbox face size"
msgid "Large"
msgstr "Mór"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:151
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label: listbox face size"
msgid "Extra Large"
msgstr "An-mhór"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:154
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"<p>Selecting <b>Extra Small</b> means the model will detect small background "
"faces in addition to medium and larger faces. Selecting <b>Small Faces</b> "
"increases the sensitivity of the model by tuning the model parameters. It "
"will also increase the probability of false-positives, and it will increase "
"detection time.</p><p>Selecting <b>Large</b> or <b>Extra Large</b> will "
"eliminate small background faces from being detected. It is much faster and "
"will reduce the number of false-positives, but will not detect small faces "
"in the background or faces in large group photos.</p><p>If you want to "
"detect all faces in one pass, select <b>Extra Small</b> faces and set the "
"detection accuracy to 2. Unfortunately, this will create a significant "
"number of false-positives. It is recommended to set a detection accuracy of "
"6-8 and face size of <b>Medium</b> or <b>Large</b> for normal use.</"
"p><p>This setting applies only to YuNet.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Má roghnaítear <b>An-Bheag</b> ciallaíonn sé sin go mbraithfidh an "
"tsamhail aghaidheanna beaga sa chúlra chomh maith le haghaidheanna "
"meánmhéide agus níos mó. Má roghnaítear <b>Aghaidheanna Beaga</b> méadaítear "
"íogaireacht an tsamhail trí pharaiméadair an tsamhail a choigeartú. Méadóidh "
"sé seo an dóchúlacht go mbeidh torthaí dearfacha bréagacha ann freisin, agus "
"méadóidh sé an t-am braite.</p><p>Má roghnaítear <b>Mór</b> nó <b>An-Mhór</"
"b>, cuirfear deireadh le braiteadh aghaidheanna beaga sa chúlra. Tá sé i "
"bhfad níos tapúla agus laghdóidh sé líon na dtorthaí dearfacha bréagacha, "
"ach ní bhraithfidh sé aghaidheanna beaga sa chúlra ná aghaidheanna i "
"ngrianghraif ghrúpa móra.</p><p>Más mian leat gach aghaidh a bhrath in aon "
"phas amháin, roghnaigh aghaidheanna <b>An-Bheag</b> agus socraigh an "
"cruinneas braite go 2. Ar an drochuair, cruthóidh sé seo líon suntasach "
"torthaí dearfacha bréagacha. Moltar cruinneas braite de 6-8 agus méid "
"aghaidhe de <b>Meánach</b> nó <b>Mór</b> a shocrú le haghaidh gnáthúsáide.</"
"p><p>Baineann an socrú seo le YuNet amháin.</p>"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:171
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title short translated text"
msgid "Detection"
msgstr "Brathadóireacht"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:180
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label short translated text about the Face Recognition Accuracy"
msgid "Accuracy:"
msgstr "Cruinneas:"

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:187
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Adjust sensitivity versus specificity: the higher the value, the more "
"accurately faces will<br>be recognized, but less faces will be recognized."
"<br>Note: only faces that are very similar to pre-tagged faces are "
"recognized."
msgstr ""
"Coigeartaigh íogaireacht i gcoinne sainiúlachta: dá airde an luach, is ea is "
"cruinne a aithneofar aghaidheanna,<br>ach aithneofar níos lú aghaidheanna."
"<br>Tabhair faoi deara: ní aithnítear ach aghaidheanna atá an-chosúil le "
"haghaidheanna réamhchlibeáilte."

#: core/libs/facesengine/widgets/facescanwidget.cpp:198
