#: core/libs/onlineversion/onlineversiondlg.cpp:274
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Current <b>%1</b> pre-release date is <i>%2</i>.</p><p>New pre-release "
"built on <i>%3</i> is available on this <a href='%4'>repository</a>.</"
"p><p>Press <b>Download</b> to get the file...</p><p>Note: from Setup/Misc "
"panel, you can switch to check for stable release only.<br>Stable versions "
"are safe to use in production.</p><p>Press <b>Configure</b> if you want to "
"customize update options from setup dialog.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Is é <i>%2</i> an dáta réamh-eisiúna reatha ar <b>%1</b>.</p><p>Tá réamh-"
"eisiúint nua atá tógtha ar <i>%3</i> ar fáil ar an <a href='%4'>stór seo</a>."
"</p><p>Brúigh <b>Íoslódáil</b> chun an comhad a fháil...</p><p>Tabhair faoi "
"deara: ón bpainéal Socrú/Ilghnéitheach, is féidir leat aistriú chuig "
"seiceáil le haghaidh scaoileadh cobhsaí amháin.<br>Tá leaganacha cobhsaí "
"sábháilte le húsáid i dtáirgeadh.</p><p>Brúigh <b>Cumraigh</b> más mian leat "
"roghanna nuashonraithe a shaincheapadh ón dialóg socraithe.</p>"

#: core/libs/onlineversion/onlineversiondlg.cpp:287
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Current <b>%1</b> stable version is <i>%2</i></p><p>New stable version <i>"
"%3</i> is available on this <a href='%4'>repository</a>.</p><p>Press "
"<b>Download</b> to get the file...</p><p>Note: from Setup/Misc panel, you "
"can switch to check for weekly pre-release.<br>Pre-release versions are "
"dedicated to test quickly new features.<br>It is not recommended to use pre-"
"releases in production as bugs can remain,<br>unless you know what you are "
"doing.</p><p>Press <b>Configure</b> if you want to customize update options "
"from setup dialog.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Is é <i>%2</i> an leagan cobhsaí reatha de <b>%1</b></p><p>Tá leagan "
"cobhsaí nua <i>%3</i> ar fáil sa <a href='%4'>stór</a> seo.</p><p>Brúigh "
"<b>Íoslódáil</b> chun an comhad a fháil...</p><p>Nóta: ón bpainéal Socrú/"
"Cineálacha, is féidir leat aistriú chun seiceáil le haghaidh réamhleagan "
"seachtainiúil.<br>Tá réamhleaganacha dírithe ar ghnéithe nua a thástáil go "
"tapa.<br>Ní mholtar réamhleaganacha a úsáid i dtáirgeadh mar d’fhéadfadh "
"fabhtanna a bheith iontu fós,<br>mura bhfuil a fhios agat cad atá á dhéanamh "
"agat.</p><p>Brúigh <b>Cumraigh</b> más mian leat roghanna nuashonraithe a "
"shaincheapadh ón dialóg socruithe.</p>"

