msgstr "AAHD"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:249
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Quality (interpolation)</title><para>Select here the demosaicing "
"method to use when decoding RAW images. A demosaicing algorithm is a digital "
"image process used to interpolate a complete image from the partial raw data "
"received from the color-filtered image sensor, internal to many digital "
"cameras, in form of a matrix of colored pixels. Also known as CFA "
"interpolation or color reconstruction, another common spelling is "
"demosaicing. The following methods are available for demosaicing RAW images:"
"</para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>Bilinear</emphasis>: use "
"high-speed but low-quality bilinear interpolation (default - for slow "
"computers). In this method, the red value of a non-red pixel is computed as "
"the average of the adjacent red pixels, and similarly for blue and green.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>VNG</emphasis>: use Variable Number of "
"Gradients interpolation. This method computes gradients near the pixel of "
"interest and uses the lower gradients (representing smoother and more "
"similar parts of the image) to make an estimate.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>PPG</emphasis>: use Patterned-Pixel-Grouping interpolation. "
"Pixel Grouping uses assumptions about natural scenery in making estimates. "
"It has fewer color artifacts on natural images than the Variable Number of "
"Gradients method.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>AHD</emphasis>: use "
"Adaptive Homogeneity-Directed interpolation. This method selects the "
"direction of interpolation so as to maximize a homogeneity metric, thus "
"typically minimizing color artifacts.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>DCB</emphasis>: DCB interpolation from linuxphoto.org project."
"</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>DHT</emphasis>: DHT interpolation.See "
"https://www.libraw.org/node/2306 for details.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>AAHD</emphasis>: modified AHD interpolation.</item></list></"
"para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Cáilíocht (idirshuíomh)</title><para>Roghnaigh anseo an modh "
"díshuíomhaithe le húsáid agus íomhánna RAW á ndíchódú. Is próiseas íomhá "
"digiteach é algartam díshuíomhaithe a úsáidtear chun íomhá iomlán a "
"idirshuíomh ó na sonraí amha páirteacha a fhaightear ón braiteoir íomhá "
"scagtha le dath, atá inmheánach i go leor ceamaraí digiteacha, i bhfoirm "
"maitrís de phicteilíní daite. Ar a dtugtar idirshuíomh CFA nó atógáil datha "
"freisin, is é díshuíomhú litriú coitianta eile. Tá na modhanna seo a leanas "
"ar fáil chun íomhánna RAW a dhíshuíomhú:</para><para><list><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Délíneach</emphasis>: bain úsáid as idirshuíomh délíneach "
"ardluais ach ísealcháilíochta (réamhshocraithe - do ríomhairí mall). Sa "
"mhodh seo, ríomhtar luach dearg picteilín neamh-dhearg mar mheán na "
"bpicteilíní dearga cóngaracha, agus ar an gcaoi chéanna le haghaidh gorm "
"agus glas.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>VNG</emphasis>: bain úsáid as "
"idirshuíomh Líon Athraitheach na nGrádán. Ríomhann an modh seo grádáin in "
"aice leis an bpicteilín spéise agus úsáideann sé na grádáin níos ísle (a "
"léiríonn codanna níos míne agus níos cosúla den íomhá) chun meastachán a "
"dhéanamh.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>PPG</emphasis>: bain úsáid as "
"idirshuíomh Grúpáil Picteilíní Patrúnaithe. Úsáideann Grúpáil Picteilíní "
"toimhdí faoi radharcra nádúrtha agus meastacháin á ndéanamh. Tá níos lú "
"déantáin datha aige ar íomhánna nádúrtha ná an modh Líon Athraitheach "
"Gradients.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>AHD</emphasis>: bain úsáid as "
"idirshuíomh Oiriúnaitheach Aonchineálachta-Dírithe. Roghnaíonn an modh seo "
"treo an idirshuímh chun méadracht aonchineála a uasmhéadú, agus ar an gcaoi "
"sin laghdaítear déantáin datha de ghnáth.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>DCB</emphasis>: Idirshuímh DCB ó thionscadal linuxphoto.org.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>DHT</emphasis>: Idirshuímh DHT. Féach "
"https://www.libraw.org/node/2306 le haghaidh sonraí.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>AAHD</emphasis>: idirshuímh AHD modhnaithe.</item></list></"
"para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:297
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider"
msgid "Pass:"
msgstr "Pas:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:298
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Pass</title><para>Set here the passes used by the median filter "
"applied after interpolation to Red-Green and Blue-Green channels.</"
"para><para>This setting is only available for specific Quality options: "
"<emphasis strong='true'>Bilinear</emphasis>, <emphasis strong='true'>VNG</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis strong='true'>PPG</emphasis>, <emphasis "
"strong='true'>AHD</emphasis>, <emphasis strong='true'>DCB</emphasis>, and "
"<emphasis strong='true'>VCD & AHD</emphasis>.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Pas</title><para>Socraigh anseo na pasanna a úsáideann an scagaire "
"meánach a chuirtear i bhfeidhm tar éis idirshuíomh ar chainéil Dhearg-Uaine "
"agus Gorm-Uaine.</para><para>Níl an socrú seo ar fáil ach amháin le haghaidh "
"roghanna Cáilíochta sonracha: <emphasis strong='true'>Délíneach</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis strong='true'>VNG</emphasis>, <emphasis strong='true'>PPG</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis strong='true'>AHD</emphasis>, <emphasis "
"strong='true'>DCB</emphasis>, agus <emphasis strong='true'>VCD & AHD</"
"emphasis>.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:310
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Refine interpolation"
msgstr "Scagaigh idirshuíomh"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:311
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Refine interpolation</title><para>This setting is available only for "
"few Quality options:</para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>DCB</"
"emphasis>: turn on the enhance interpolated colors filter.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>VCD & AHD</emphasis>: turn on the "
"enhanced effective color interpolation (EECI) refine to improve sharpness.</"
"item></list></para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Mionchoigeartú idirshuíomh</title><para>Níl an socrú seo ar fáil ach "
"do roinnt roghanna Cáilíochta:</para><para><list><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>DCB</emphasis>: cuir an scagaire feabhsaithe dathanna "
"idirshuíomhaithe i ngníomh.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>VCD & AHD</"
"emphasis>: cuir an mionchoigeartú feabhsaithe idirshuíomh datha éifeachtach "
"(EECI) i ngníomh chun géire a fheabhsú.</item></list></para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:324
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Demosaicing"
msgstr "Dí-mhaoisiú"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:332
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:listbox"
msgid "Method:"
msgstr "Modh:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:334
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox"
msgid "Default D65"
msgstr "Réamhshocrú D65"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:335
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox"
msgid "Camera"
msgstr "Ceamara"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:336
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox set while balance automatically"
msgid "Automatic"
msgstr "Uathoibríoch"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:337
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox set white balance manually"
msgid "Manual"
msgstr "De Láimh"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:339
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>White Balance</title><para>Configure the raw white balance:</"
"para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>Default D65</emphasis>: Use a "
"standard daylight D65 white balance.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Camera</emphasis>: Use the white balance specified by the "
"camera. If not available, reverts to default neutral white balance.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Automatic</emphasis>: Calculates an "
"automatic white balance averaging the entire image.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Manual</emphasis>: Set a custom temperature and green level "
"values.</item></list></para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Cothromaíocht Bhán</title><para>Cumraigh an chothromaíocht bhán amh:</"
"para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>Réamhshocrú D65</emphasis>: "
"Úsáid cothromaíocht bhán caighdeánach D65 i solas an lae.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Ceamara</emphasis>: Úsáid an "
"chothromaíocht bhán atá sonraithe ag an gceamara. Mura bhfuil sé ar fáil, "
"filleann sé ar an gcothromaíocht bhán neodrach réamhshocraithe.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Uathoibríoch</emphasis>: Ríomhann sé "
"cothromaíocht bhán uathoibríoch a mheasann meán iomlán na híomhá.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Lámhleabhar</emphasis>: Socraigh "
"luachanna saincheaptha teochta agus leibhéal glas.</item></list></para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:354
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider"
msgid "T(K):"
msgstr "T(K):"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:355
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Temperature</title><para>Set here the color temperature in Kelvin.</"
"para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Teocht</title><para>Socraigh anseo an teocht datha i gCelvin.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:362
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider Green component"
msgid "Green:"
msgstr "Uaine:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:363
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<para>Set here the green component to set magenta color cast removal level.</"
"para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Socraigh anseo an chomhpháirt ghlas chun leibhéal bainte teilgean "
"datha magenta a shocrú.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:366
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:listbox"
msgid "Highlights:"
msgstr "Buaicphointí:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:368
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox"
msgid "Solid white"
msgstr "Bán soladach"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:369
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox"
msgid "Unclip"
msgstr "Díghlasáil"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:370
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox"
msgid "Blend"
msgstr "Cumasc"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:371
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox"
msgid "Rebuild"
msgstr "Aththógáil"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:373
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Highlights</title><para>Select here the highlight clipping method:</"
"para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>Solid white</emphasis>: clip "
"all highlights to solid white</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Unclip</"
"emphasis>: leave highlights unclipped in various shades of pink</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Blend</emphasis>:Blend clipped and "
"unclipped values together for a gradual fade to white</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Rebuild</emphasis>: reconstruct highlights using a level "
"value</item></list></para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Buaicphointí</title><para>Roghnaigh anseo an modh gearrtha "
"buaicphointí:</para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>Bán soladach</"
"emphasis>: gearr na buaicphointí go léir go bán soladach</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Díghearradh</emphasis>: fág buaicphointí "
"gan ghearradh i ndathanna éagsúla bándearg</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Cumasc</emphasis>:Cumasc luachanna gearrtha agus "
"neamhghearrtha le chéile le haghaidh céimniú de réir a chéile go bán</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Atógáil</emphasis>: atóg buaicphointí ag "
"baint úsáide as luach leibhéalta</item></list></para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:384
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider Highlight reconstruct level"
msgid "Level:"
msgstr "Leibhéal:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:388
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Level</title><para>Specify the reconstruct highlight level. Low "
"values favor whites and high values favor colors.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Leibhéal</title><para>Sonraigh an leibhéal aibhsithe atógála. Is "
"fearr le luachanna ísle bán agus is fearr le luachanna arda dathanna.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:392
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Exposure Correction (E.V)"
msgstr "Ceartú Nochta (E.V)"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:393
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid "<para>Turn on the exposure correction before interpolation.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Cas an ceartú nochta air roimh idirshuíomh.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:396
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider"
msgid "Linear Shift:"
msgstr "Aistriú Líneach:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:401
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Shift</title><para>Linear Shift of exposure correction before "
"interpolation in E.V</para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Aistriú</title><para>Aistriú Líneach ar cheartú nochta roimh "
"idirshuíomh in E.V</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:404
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider"
msgid "Highlight:"
msgstr "Buaicphointe:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:409
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Highlight</title><para>Amount of highlight preservation for exposure "
"correction before interpolation in E.V. Only take effect if Shift Correction "
"is > 1.0 E.V</para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Aibhsiú</title><para>Méid caomhnaithe aibhsithe le haghaidh ceartú "
"nochta roimh idirshuíomh in E.V. Ní thiocfaidh sé i bhfeidhm ach amháin má "
"tá an Ceartú Aistrithe > 1.0 E.V</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:413
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Correct false colors in highlights"
msgstr "Ceartaigh dathanna bréagacha i mbuaicphointí"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:414
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<para>If enabled, images with overblown channels are processed much more "
"accurately, without 'pink clouds' (and blue highlights under tungsten lamps)."
"</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Má tá sé cumasaithe, déantar íomhánna le bealaí ró-shéidte a "
"phróiseáil i bhfad níos cruinne, gan 'scamaill bándearga' (agus buaicphointí "
"gorma faoi lampaí tungstain).</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:418
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Auto Brightness"
msgstr "Gile Uathoibríoch"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:419
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<para>If disable, use a fixed white level and ignore the image histogram to "
"adjust brightness.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Más rud é go bhfuil sé díchumasaithe, bain úsáid as leibhéal bán "
"seasta agus déan neamhaird den histagram íomhá chun gile a choigeartú.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:422
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:slider"
msgid "Brightness:"
msgstr "Gile:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:427
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Brightness</title><para>Specify the brightness level of output image. "
"The default value is 1.0 (works in 8-bit mode only).</para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Gile</title><para>Sonraigh leibhéal gile na híomhá aschuir. Is é 1.0 "
"an luach réamhshocraithe (oibríonn sé i mód 8-giotán amháin).</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:437
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check Black point"
msgid "Black:"
msgstr "Dubh:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:438
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Black point</title><para>Use a specific black point value to decode "
"RAW pictures. If you set this option to off, the Black Point value will be "
"automatically computed.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Pointe dubh</title><para>Úsáid luach pointe dubh ar leith chun "
"pictiúir RAW a dhíchódú. Má shocraíonn tú an rogha seo, ríomhfar luach an "
"Phointe Dhuibh go huathoibríoch.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:445
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Black point value</title><para>Specify specific black point value of "
"the output image.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Luach pointe dubh</title><para>Sonraigh luach pointe dubh sonrach na "
"híomhá aschuir.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:448
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check White point"
msgid "White:"
msgstr "Bán:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:449
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>White point</title><para>Use a specific white point value to decode "
"RAW pictures. If you set this option to off, the White Point value will be "
"automatically computed.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Pointe bán</title><para>Úsáid luach pointe bán ar leith chun pictiúir "
"RAW a dhíchódú. Má shocraíonn tú an rogha seo, ríomhfar luach an Phointe "
"Bháin go huathoibríoch.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:456
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>White point value</title><para>Specify specific white point value of "
"the output image.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Luach pointe bán</title><para>Sonraigh luach pointe bán sonrach na "
"híomhá aschuir.</para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:496
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "White Balance"
msgstr "Cothromaíocht Bhán"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:504
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:listbox"
msgid "Noise reduction:"
msgstr "Laghdú torainn:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:506
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Noise Reduction"
msgid "None"
msgstr "Dada"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:507
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Noise Reduction"
msgid "Wavelets"
msgstr "Tonnta"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:508
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Noise Reduction"
msgid "FBDD"
msgstr "FBDD"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:510
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Noise Reduction</title><para>Select here the noise reduction method "
"to apply during RAW decoding.</para><para><list><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>None</emphasis>: no noise reduction.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Wavelets</emphasis>: wavelets correction to erase noise while "
"preserving real detail. It is applied after interpolation.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>FBDD</emphasis>: Fake Before Demosaicing "
"Denoising noise reduction. It is applied before interpolation.</item></"
"list></para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Laghdú Torainn</title><para>Roghnaigh anseo an modh laghdaithe "
"torainn le cur i bhfeidhm le linn díchódú RAW.</"
"para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>Gan aon cheann</emphasis>: "
"gan aon laghdú torainn.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Tonnta beaga</"
"emphasis>: ceartú tonnta beaga chun torann a scriosadh agus fíor-shonraí á "
"gcaomhnú. Cuirtear i bhfeidhm é tar éis idirshuíomh.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>FBDD</emphasis>: Bréige Roimh Dhí-thosú Laghdú torainn dí-"
"thosaithe. Cuirtear i bhfeidhm é roimh idirshuíomh.</item></list></para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:535
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Corrections"
msgstr "Ceartúcháin"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:543
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:listbox"
msgid "Camera Profile:"
msgstr "Próifíl Ceamara:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:545
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Camera Profile"
msgid "None"
msgstr "Dada"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:546
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Camera Profile"
msgid "Embedded"
msgstr "Leabaithe"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:547
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Camera Profile"
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Saincheaptha"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:549
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Camera Profile</title><para>Select here the input color space used to "
"decode RAW data.</para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>None</"
"emphasis>: no input color profile is used during RAW decoding.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Embedded</emphasis>: use embedded color "
"profile from RAW file, if it exists.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Custom</emphasis>: use a custom input color space profile.</"
"item></list></para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Próifíl Ceamara</title><para>Roghnaigh anseo an spás datha ionchuir a "
"úsáidtear chun sonraí RAW a dhíchódú.</para><para><list><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Gan aon cheann</emphasis>: ní úsáidtear aon phróifíl datha "
"ionchuir le linn díchódú RAW.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Leabaithe</"
"emphasis>: bain úsáid as próifíl datha leabaithe ó chomhad RAW, más ann di.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Saincheaptha</emphasis>: bain úsáid as "
"próifíl spás datha ionchuir saincheaptha.</item></list></para>"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:560
#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:594
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info: open file filters"
msgid "ICC Files (*.icc *.icm)"
msgstr "Comhaid ICC (*.icc *.icm)"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:562
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:listbox"
msgid "Workspace:"
msgstr "Spás Oibre:"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:564
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Workspace"
msgid "Raw (no profile)"
msgstr "Amh (gan phróifíl)"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:565
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Workspace"
msgid "sRGB"
msgstr "sRGB"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:566
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Workspace"
msgid "Adobe RGB"
msgstr "Adobe RGB"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:567
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Workspace"
msgid "Wide Gamut"
msgstr "Gamut Leathan"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:568
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Workspace"
msgid "Pro-Photo"
msgstr "Grianghrafadóireacht Ghairmiúil"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:569
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:inlistbox Workspace"
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Saincheaptha"

#: core/libs/rawengine/drawdecoderwidget.cpp:571
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<title>Workspace</title><para>Select here the output color space used to "
"decode RAW data.</para><para><list><item><emphasis strong='true'>Raw "
"(linear)</emphasis>: in this mode, no output color space is used during RAW "
"decoding.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>sRGB</emphasis>: this is an "
"RGB color space, created cooperatively by Hewlett-Packard and Microsoft. It "
"is the best choice for images destined for the Web and portrait photography."
"</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Adobe RGB</emphasis>: this color space "
"is an extended RGB color space, developed by Adobe. It is used for "
"photography applications such as advertising and fine art.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Wide Gamut</emphasis>: this color space "
"is an expanded version of the Adobe RGB color space.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Pro-Photo</emphasis>: this color space is an RGB color space, "
"developed by Kodak, that offers an especially large gamut designed for use "
"with photographic outputs in mind.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Custom</emphasis>: use a custom output color space profile.</"
"item></list></para>"
msgstr ""
"<title>Spás Oibre</title><para>Roghnaigh anseo an spás datha aschuir a "
"úsáidtear chun sonraí RAW a dhíchódú.</para><para><list><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Amh (líneach)</emphasis>: sa mhodh seo, ní úsáidtear aon spás "
"datha aschuir le linn díchódú RAW.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>sRGB</"
"emphasis>: is spás datha RGB é seo, arna chruthú i gcomhar le Hewlett-"
"Packard agus Microsoft. Is é an rogha is fearr é d'íomhánna atá beartaithe "
"don Ghréasán agus do ghrianghrafadóireacht portráide.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>Adobe RGB</emphasis>: is spás datha RGB leathnaithe é an spás "
"datha seo, arna fhorbairt ag Adobe. Úsáidtear é le haghaidh feidhmchlár "
"grianghrafadóireachta amhail fógraíocht agus ealaín mhín.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Gamut Leathan</emphasis>: is leagan "
"leathnaithe den spás datha Adobe RGB an spás datha seo.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Pro-Photo</emphasis>: is spás datha RGB é "
"an spás datha seo, arna fhorbairt ag Kodak, a thairgeann gamut thar a bheith "
"mór atá deartha lena úsáid le haschur grianghrafadóireachta san áireamh.</"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>Saincheaptha</emphasis>: bain úsáid as "
"próifíl spás datha aschuir saincheaptha.</item></list></para>"

