msgstr "/Pictures"

#: core/utilities/firstrun/collectionpage.cpp:77
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Please enter a location where you keep your images.</p> <p>You can choose "
"any local folder, even one that already contains images.<br> More folders "
"can be added later under the <i>Settings</i> menu. </p> "
msgstr ""
"<p>Cuir isteach suíomh ina gcoinníonn tú do chuid íomhánna.</p> <p>Is féidir "
"leat aon fhillteán áitiúil a roghnú, fiú ceann ina bhfuil íomhánna cheana "
"féin.<br> Is féidir tuilleadh fillteán a chur leis níos déanaí faoin "
"roghchlár <i>Socruithe</i>.</p> "

#: core/utilities/firstrun/collectionpage.cpp:85
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p><i>Note:</i> removable media (such as USB drives or DVDs) and remote file "
"systems (such as NFS, or Samba mounted with cifs/smbfs) are supported.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p><i>Nóta:</i> Tacaítear le meáin inbhainte (amhail tiomántáin USB nó "
"DVDanna) agus córais chomhad iargúlta (amhail NFS, nó Samba atá feistithe le "
"cifs/smbfs).</p>"

#: core/utilities/firstrun/collectionpage.cpp:148
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You must select a folder for digiKam to use as the root album. All of your "
"images will go there."
msgstr ""
"Ní mór duit fillteán a roghnú le húsáid ag digiKam mar an albam fréimhe. "
"Rachaidh do chuid íomhánna go léir ann."

