msgstr "Uasmhéid bearna ama (uu:nn:ss):"

#: core/utilities/geolocation/geoiface/correlator/gpscorrelatorwidget.cpp:194
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Sets the maximum time difference to interpolate GPX file points to image "
"time data. If the time difference exceeds this setting, no match will be "
"attempted."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn sé an difríocht ama uasta chun pointí comhaid GPX a idirshuíomh le "
"sonraí ama íomhá. Mura sáraíonn an difríocht ama an socrú seo, ní dhéanfar "
"aon iarracht meaitseáil."

