"gceart nuair a thógtar pictiúir. Sábhálfar na luachanna sna clibeanna EXIF, "
"XMP, agus IPTC DateTimeDigitized agus DateTimeCreated."

#: core/utilities/import/widgets/advancedsettings.cpp:142
