#: core/utilities/setup/collections/setupcollections.cpp:86
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Below are the locations of your root albums used to store your images. "
"Write access is necessary to be able to edit images in these albums.</"
"p><p>Note: Removable media (such as USB drives or DVDs) and remote file "
"systems (such as NFS, or Samba mounted with cifs/smbfs) are supported.</"
"p><p>Important: You need to mount the share natively on your system before "
"to setup a remote collection.</p><p></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Seo thíos suíomhanna d’albam fréimhe a úsáidtear chun d’íomhánna a "
"stóráil. Tá rochtain scríbhneoireachta riachtanach chun íomhánna a chur in "
"eagar sna halbaim seo.</p><p>Nóta: Tacaítear le meáin inbhainte (mar shampla "
"tiomántáin USB nó DVDanna) agus córais chomhad iargúlta (mar shampla NFS, nó "
"Samba atá feistithe le cifs/smbfs).</p><p>Tábhachtach: Ní mór duit an "
"comhroinnt a fheistiú go dúchasach ar do chóras sula socraíonn tú bailiúchán "
"iargúlta.</p><p></p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/collections/setupcollections.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Below are the locations of your root albums used to store your images. "
