msgstr ""
"<b>Nóta: Ídíonn monatóireacht albam acmhainní an chórais agus is féidir léi "
"digiKam a mhoilliú. Mura bhfuil tú ag úsáid macOS agus bailiúcháin líonra, "
"níor cheart duit monatóireacht albam a ghníomhachtú.</b>"

#: core/utilities/setup/collections/setupcollections.cpp:129
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:tab"
msgid "Root Album Folders"
msgstr "Fillteáin Albam Fréamhacha"

#: core/utilities/setup/collections/setupcollections.cpp:136
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Set the names of directories that you want to ignore from your photo "
"collections. The names are case sensitive and should be separated by a "
"semicolon.</p><p>This is for example useful when you store your photos on a "
"Synology NAS (Network Attached Storage). In every directory the system "
"creates a subdirectory @eaDir to store thumbnails. To avoid digiKam "
"inserting the original photo and its corresponding thumbnail twice, @eaDir "
"is ignored by default.</p><p>Wildcard characters such as '*' or '?' are "
"supported.</p><p>To re-include directories that are ignored by default "
"prefix it with a minus, e.g. -@eaDir.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Socraigh ainmneacha na n-eolaire ar mhaith leat neamhaird a dhéanamh "
"orthu i do bhailiúcháin grianghraf. Tá na hainmneacha íogair ó thaobh cás de "
"agus ba chóir iad a dheighilt le leathstad.</p><p>Tá sé seo úsáideach mar "
"shampla nuair a stórálann tú do ghrianghraif ar Synology NAS (Stóráil "
"Ceangailte Líonra). I ngach eolaire cruthaíonn an córas fo-eolaire @eaDir "
"chun mionsamhlacha a stóráil. Chun a sheachaint go gcuirfidh digiKam an "
"grianghraf bunaidh agus a mhionsamhlacha comhfhreagrach isteach faoi dhó, "
"déantar neamhaird de @eaDir de réir réamhshocraithe.</p><p>Tacaítear le "
"carachtair fhiáine ar nós '*' nó '?'.</p><p>Chun eolairí a ath-áireamh a "
"ndéantar neamhaird orthu de réir réamhshocraithe, cuir lúide leis an réimír, "
"m.sh. -@eaDir.</p>"

