#: core/utilities/setup/editor/setupversioning.cpp:461
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>JPEG</emphasis>: It is the most commonly used "
"file format, but it employs lossy compression, which means that with each "
"saving operation some image information will be irreversibly lost. JPEG "
"offers a good compression rate, resulting in smaller files. </"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>PNG</emphasis>: A widely used format "
"employing lossless compression. The files, though, will be larger because "
"PNG does not achieve very good compression rates.</item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>TIFF</emphasis>: A commonly used format, usually uncompressed "
"or with modest lossless compression. Resulting files will be large, but "
"without quality loss due to compression. </item><item><emphasis "
"strong='true'>PGF</emphasis>: This is a technically superior file format "
"offering good compression rates with either lossy or lossless compression. "
"But it is not yet widely used and supported, so your friends may not "
"directly be able to open these files, and you may not be able to directly "
"publish them on the web. </item>"
msgstr ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>JPEG</emphasis>: Is í an fhormáid comhaid is "
"coitianta a úsáidtear í, ach úsáideann sí comhbhrú caillteanach, rud a "
"chiallaíonn go gcaillfear roinnt faisnéise íomhá go dochúlaithe le gach "
"oibríocht sábhála. Cuireann JPEG ráta comhbhrúite maith ar fáil, rud a "
"fhágann comhaid níos lú. </item><item><emphasis strong='true'>PNG</"
"emphasis>: Formáid a úsáidtear go forleathan a úsáideann comhbhrú gan "
"chailliúint. Beidh na comhaid níos mó, áfach, toisc nach mbainfidh PNG rátaí "
"comhbhrúite an-mhaith amach.</item><item><emphasis strong='true'>TIFF</"
"emphasis>: Formáid a úsáidtear go coitianta, de ghnáth gan chomhbhrú nó le "
"comhbhrú measartha gan chailliúint. Beidh na comhaid a eascraíonn as sin "
"mór, ach gan aon chaillteanas cáilíochta mar gheall ar chomhbhrú. </"
"item><item><emphasis strong='true'>PGF</emphasis>: Is formáid comhaid níos "
"fearr ó thaobh na teicneolaíochta de í seo a thairgeann rátaí comhbhrúite "
"maithe le comhbhrú caillteanach nó gan chailliúint. Ach níl sé in úsáid agus "
"tacaithe go forleathan fós, mar sin b'fhéidir nach mbeidh do chairde in ann "
"na comhaid seo a oscailt go díreach, agus b'fhéidir nach mbeidh tú in ann "
"iad a fhoilsiú go díreach ar an ngréasán.</item>"

#: core/utilities/setup/editor/setupversioning.cpp:494
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>JPEG-2000</emphasis>: It is similar to PGF. "
"Loading or saving is slower, the compression rate is better, and the format "
"more widely supported, though still not comparable to the tradition formats "
"JPEG, PNG or TIFF. </item>"
msgstr ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>JPEG-2000</emphasis>: Tá sé cosúil le PGF. Tá "
"an luchtú nó an sábháil níos moille, tá an ráta comhbhrúite níos fearr, agus "
"tá tacaíocht níos forleithne don fhormáid, cé nach bhfuil sé inchomparáide "
"fós leis na formáidí traidisiúnta JPEG, PNG nó TIFF.</item>"

#: core/utilities/setup/editor/setupversioning.cpp:506
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>HEIF</emphasis>: High Efficiency Image File "
"Format is a container format for storing individual images. A HEIF image "
"using HEVC codec (H.265) requires less storage space than the equivalent "
"quality JPEG. </item>"
msgstr ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>HEIF</emphasis>: Is formáid choimeádáin í "
"Formáid Comhaid Íomhá Ard-Éifeachtúlachta chun íomhánna aonair a stóráil. "
"Éilíonn íomhá HEIF a úsáideann códc HEVC (H.265) níos lú spáis stórála ná an "
"JPEG den chaighdeán coibhéiseach.</item>"

#: core/utilities/setup/editor/setupversioning.cpp:517
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>JPEG-XL</emphasis>: It is a royalty-free "
"raster-graphics file format that supports lossless compression. It is "
"designed to outperform existing raster formats and thus to become their "
"universal replacement. </item>"
msgstr ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>JPEG-XL</emphasis>: Is formáid comhaid raster-"
"grafaicí saor ó ríchíosanna í a thacaíonn le comhbhrú gan chailliúint. Tá sí "
"deartha chun feidhmiú níos fearr ná formáidí raster atá ann cheana féin agus "
"dá bhrí sin chun bheith ina hionad uilíoch dóibh.</item>"

#: core/utilities/setup/editor/setupversioning.cpp:527
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>WEBP</emphasis>: It is an image file format "
"that Google has developed as a replacement for JPEG, PNG, and GIF file "
"formats. Files are smaller for the same quality, or of higher quality for "
"the same size. It supports both lossy and lossless compression</item>"
msgstr ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>WEBP</emphasis>: Is formáid comhaid íomhá í "
"atá forbartha ag Google mar ionadach do na formáidí comhaid JPEG, PNG, agus "
"GIF. Bíonn comhaid níos lú don cháilíocht chéanna, nó níos airde don mhéid "
"chéanna. Tacaíonn sé le comhbhrú caillteanais agus gan chaillteanas araon.</"
"item>"

#: core/utilities/setup/editor/setupversioning.cpp:538
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>AVIF</emphasis>: AV1 Image File Format is a "
"specification for storing images in the ISOBMFF container (as HEIF) "
"compressed with AOMedia Video 1 (AV1) codec, an open and royalty-free "
"encoding format. </item>"
msgstr ""
"<item><emphasis strong='true'>AVIF</emphasis>: Is sonraíocht í Formáid "
"Comhaid Íomhá AV1 chun íomhánna a stóráil sa choimeádán ISOBMFF (mar HEIF) "
"atá comhbhrúite le códac AOMedia Video 1 (AV1), formáid ionchódaithe "
"oscailte agus saor ó ríchíosanna.</item>"

