msgstr "Spás Dath Oibre"

#: core/utilities/setup/icc/setupicc.cpp:66
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>This is the color space all the images will be converted to when opened "
"(if you choose to convert) and the profile that will be embedded when "
"saving. Good and safe choices are <b>Adobe RGB (1998)</b> and <b>sRGB "
"IEC61966-2.1</b></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Seo an spás datha a ndéanfar na híomhánna go léir a thiontú chuige nuair "
"a osclaítear iad (má roghnaíonn tú tiontú) agus an phróifíl a leabófar nuair "
"a shábhálfar iad. Is roghanna maithe agus sábháilte iad <b>Adobe RGB (1998)</"
"b> agus <b>sRGB IEC61966-2.1</b></p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/icc/setupicc.cpp:72
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>You can use this button to get more detailed information about the "
"selected workspace profile.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Is féidir leat an cnaipe seo a úsáid chun tuilleadh eolais mhionsonraithe "
"a fháil faoin bpróifíl spás oibre roghnaithe.</p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/icc/setupicc.cpp:86
#, kde-format
