#, kde-format
msgid "Monitor profile:"
msgstr "Próifíl monatóireachta:"

#: core/utilities/setup/icc/setupicc.cpp:226
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>If your desktop do not provide a color profile for your screen, select "
"here the default one. If no profile is set, sRGB will be used as fail-back. "
"In all cases, the color management workflow will try to get in first the "
"profile set for your monitor in your the desktop</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Mura soláthraíonn do dheasc próifíl datha chun do scáileán, roghnaigh an "
"ceann réamhshocraithe anseo. Mura bhfuil aon phróifíl socraithe, úsáidfear "
"sRGB mar rogha teipe. I ngach cás, déanfaidh an sreabhadh oibre "
"bainistíochta datha iarracht an phróifíl atá socraithe chun do mhonatóir a "
"chur isteach ar do dheasc ar dtús</p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/icc/setupicc.cpp:234
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>You can use this button to get more detailed information about the "
"selected monitor profile.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Is féidir leat an cnaipe seo a úsáid chun tuilleadh eolais mhionsonraithe "
"a fháil faoin bpróifíl monatóireachta roghnaithe.</p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/icc/setupicc.cpp:238
#, kde-format
