msgstr ""
"<p>Cuardaíonn digiKam próifílí ICC i bhfillteáin chórais réamhshocraithe "
"agus seolann sé cúpla próifíl roghnaithe leis féin. Stóráil do phróifílí "
"datha breise go léir san eolaire atá socraithe anseo.</p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/icc/setupicc.cpp:348
#, kde-format
msgid "Use black point compensation"
msgstr "Úsáid cúiteamh pointe dubh"

#: core/utilities/setup/icc/setupicc.cpp:349
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p><b>Black Point Compensation</b> is a way to make adjustments between the "
"maximum black levels of digital files and the black capabilities of various "
"digital devices.</p>"
msgstr ""
"Is bealach é <p><b>Cúiteamh Pointe Dubh</b> chun coigeartuithe a dhéanamh "
"idir na leibhéil dubha uasta i gcomhaid dhigiteacha agus cumais dhubha "
"gléasanna digiteacha éagsúla.</p>"

