#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/namespaceeditdlg.cpp:230
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>To create new namespaces, you need to specify parameters:</"
"p><p><ul><li>Namespace name with dots.<br>Ex.: <i>\"Xmp.digiKam.TagsList\"</"
"i></li><li>Separator parameter, used by tag paths <br>Ex.: \"City/Paris\" or "
"\"City|Paris\"</li><li>Specify if only keyword or the whole path must be "
"written.</li></ul></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Chun ainmspásanna nua a chruthú, ní mór duit paraiméadair a shonrú:</"
"p><p><ul><li>Ainm an ainmspáis le poncanna.<br>M.sh.: <i>\"Xmp.digiKam."
"TagsList\"</i></li><li>Paraiméadar deighilteora, a úsáideann cosáin "
"clibeanna <br>M.sh.: \"Cathair/Páras\" nó \"Cathair|Páras\"</li><li>Sonraigh "
"an gá ach an eochairfhocal nó an cosán iomlán a scríobh.</li></ul></p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/namespaceeditdlg.cpp:241
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>To create new rating namespaces, you need to specify parameters:</"
"p><p><ul><li>Namespace name with dots.<br>Ex.: <i>\"Xmp.xmp.Rating\"</i></"
"li><li>Rating mappings, if namespace need other values than 0-5 <br>Ex.: "
"Microsoft uses 0 1 25 50 75 99</li><li>Select the correct namespace option "
"from list.</li></ul></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Chun ainmspásanna rátála nua a chruthú, ní mór duit paraiméadair a shonrú:"
"</p><p><ul><li>Ainm an ainmspáis le poncanna.<br>M.sh.: <i>\"Xmp.xmp.Rating"
"\"</i></li><li>Mapálacha rátála, má theastaíonn luachanna eile ón ainmspás "
"seachas 0-5 <br>M.sh.: Úsáideann Microsoft 0 1 25 50 75 99</li><li>Roghnaigh "
"an rogha ainmspáis cheart ón liosta.</li></ul></p>"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/namespaceeditdlg.cpp:252
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>To create new comment namespaces, you need to specify parameters:</"
"p><p><ul><li>Namespace name with dots.<br>Ex.: <i>\"Xmp.xmp.Comment\"</i></"
"li><li>Select the correct namespace option from list.</li></ul></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Chun ainmspásanna tráchta nua a chruthú, ní mór duit paraiméadair a "
"shonrú:</p><p><ul><li>Ainm an ainmspáis le poncanna.<br>M.sh.: <i>\"Xmp.xmp."
"Comment\"</i></li><li>Roghnaigh an rogha ainmspáis cheart ón liosta.</li></"
"ul></p>"

