#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:59
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:tab advanced metadata config view"
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Ardleibhéil"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:249
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"You should only activate this option if you are exchanging image metadata "
"with programs that use the sidecar format BASENAME.xmp. If you have images "
"with the same base name (e.g. Image.CR2 and Image.JPG) then the sidecar can "
"no longer be uniquely assigned and will be used for both images, which can "
"lead to metadata problems."
msgstr ""
"Níor cheart duit an rogha seo a ghníomhachtú ach amháin má tá tú ag malartú "
"meiteashonraí íomhánna le cláir a úsáideann an fhormáid taobhlíne BASENAME."
"xmp. Má tá íomhánna agat leis an mbunainm céanna (e.g. Image.CR2 agus Image."
"JPG) ní féidir an taobhlíne a shannadh go huathúil a thuilleadh agus "
"úsáidfear í don dá íomhá, rud a d’fhéadfadh fadhbanna meiteashonraí a bheith "
"mar thoradh air."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:267
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Switching off exif auto rotation will most probably show your images in a "
"wrong orientation, so only change this option if you explicitly require this."
msgstr ""
"Is dóichí go dtaispeánfar d’íomhánna i dtreoshuíomh mícheart má mhúchtar "
"rothlú uathoibríoch exif, mar sin ná hathraigh an rogha seo ach amháin má "
"theastaíonn sé sin uait go sainráite."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:290
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Do you really want to enable metadata writing to RAW files? digiKam "
"delegates this task to the ExifTool backend.\n"
"With different RAW formats, problems are known which can lead to the corrupt "
"of RAW files.\n"
"If you decide to do so, make a backup of your RAW files. We strongly "
"recommend not to enable this option."
msgstr ""
"An bhfuil tú cinnte gur mian leat scríobh meiteashonraí chuig comhaid RAW a "
"chumasú? Tarmligeann digiKam an tasc seo chuig cúltaca ExifTool.\n"
"Le formáidí RAW éagsúla, is eol fadhbanna a d'fhéadfadh truailliú comhad RAW "
"a bheith mar thoradh orthu.\n"
"Má shocraíonn tú é sin a dhéanamh, déan cúltaca de do chuid comhad RAW. "
"Molaimid go láidir gan an rogha seo a chumasú."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:298
#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:350
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Yes I Understand"
msgstr "Sea, tuigim"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:308
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "You would rather disable writing metadata to RAW files?"
msgstr "B’fhearr leat scríobh meiteashonraí chuig comhaid AMH a dhíchumasú?"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata.cpp:345
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"A RAW file extension has been added to the list of supported sidecars. There "
"is a risk of accidentally deleting RAW images. Are you sure you want to do "
"that?"
msgstr ""
"Cuireadh síneadh comhaid RAW leis an liosta de na comhaid taobh a dtacaítear "
"leo. Tá baol ann go scriosfar íomhánna RAW de thaisme. An bhfuil tú cinnte "
"gur mhaith leat é sin a dhéanamh?"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:31
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option"
msgid "Baloo Desktop Search"
msgstr "Cuardach Deisce Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:35
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option"
msgid "Store metadata from digiKam in Baloo"
msgstr "Stóráil meiteashonraí ó digiKam i Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:36
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to push rating, comments and tags from digiKam into the "
"Baloo storage"
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun rátálacha, tuairimí agus clibeanna a bhrú ó "
"digiKam isteach sa stóras Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:40
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option"
msgid "Read metadata from Baloo"
msgstr "Léigh meiteashonraí ó Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:41
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option if you want to apply changes to rating, comments and "
"tags made in Baloo to digiKam's metadata storage. Please note that image "
"metadata will not be edited automatically."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo más mian leat athruithe ar rátáil, tuairimí agus "
"clibeanna a rinneadh i Baloo a chur i bhfeidhm ar stóras meiteashonraí "
"digiKam. Tabhair faoi deara nach ndéanfar meiteashonraí íomhá a chur in "
"eagar go huathoibríoch."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:63
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"provides the basis to handle all kinds of metadata on the KDE desktop in a "
"generic fashion. It allows you to tag, rate and comment your files in KDE "
"applications like Dolphin. Please set here if you want to synchronize the "
"metadata stored by digiKam desktop-wide with the Baloo Desktop Search."
msgstr ""
"Soláthraíonn sé an bunús chun gach cineál meiteashonraí ar dheasc KDE a "
"láimhseáil ar bhealach ginearálta. Ligeann sé duit do chuid comhad a "
"chlibeáil, a rátáil agus a thráchtáil in iarratais KDE cosúil le Dolphin. "
"Socraigh anseo más mian leat na meiteashonraí atá stóráilte ag digiKam ar "
"fud na deisce a shioncrónú le Cuardach Deisce Baloo."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_baloo.cpp:84
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:tab"
msgid "Baloo"
msgstr "Baloo"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:34
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<para>In addition to the pixel content, image files usually contain a "
"variety of metadata. A lot of the parameters you can use in digiKam to "
"manage files, such as rating or comment, can be written to the files' "
"metadata.</para> <para>Storing in metadata allows one to preserve this "
"information when moving or sending the files to different systems.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Chomh maith leis an ábhar picteilíní, bíonn meiteashonraí éagsúla i "
"gcomhaid íomhá de ghnáth. Is féidir go leor de na paraiméadair is féidir "
"leat a úsáid i digiKam chun comhaid a bhainistiú, amhail rátáil nó trácht, a "
"scríobh chuig meiteashonraí na gcomhad.</para> <para>Ligeann stóráil sna "
"meiteashonraí duit an fhaisnéis seo a chaomhnú agus na comhaid á mbogadh nó "
"á seoladh chuig córais éagsúla.</para>"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:44
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Write This Information to the Metadata"
msgstr "Scríobh an Fhaisnéis seo chuig na Meiteashonraí"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:49
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Image tags"
msgstr "Clibeanna íomhá"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:50
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid "Turn on this option to store the item tags in the XMP and IPTC tags."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun na clibeanna míre a stóráil sna clibeanna XMP agus "
"IPTC."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:54
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Captions and title"
msgstr "Foscríbhinní agus teideal"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:55
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to store item caption and title in the JFIF Comment "
"section, the Exif tag, the XMP tag, and the IPTC tag."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun fotheideal agus teideal míre a stóráil sa rannóg "
"Trácht JFIF, sa chlib Exif, sa chlib XMP, agus sa chlib IPTC."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:60
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Rating"
msgstr "Rátáil"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:61
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to store the item rating in the Exif tag and the XMP "
"tags."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun rátáil na míre a stóráil sa chlib Exif agus sna "
"clibeanna XMP."

# Not "Roghnaigh lipéad"
#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:65
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Pick label"
msgstr "Lipéad roghnaithe"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:66
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid "Turn on this option to store the item pick label in the XMP tags."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun lipéad roghnaithe na míre a stóráil sna clibeanna "
"XMP."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:70
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Color label"
msgstr "Lipéad datha"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:71
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid "Turn on this option to store the item color label in the XMP tags."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun lipéad datha an earra a stóráil sna clibeanna XMP."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:75
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Timestamps"
msgstr "Stampaí ama"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:76
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to store the item date and time in the EXIF, XMP, and "
"IPTC tags."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun dáta agus am na míre a stóráil sna clibeanna EXIF, "
"XMP, agus IPTC."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:80
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Metadata templates (Copyright etc.)"
msgstr "Teimpléid meiteashonraí (Cóipcheart, srl.)"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:81
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to store the metadata template in the XMP and the IPTC "
"tags. You can set template values to Template setup page."
msgstr ""
"Cumasaigh an rogha seo chun an teimpléad meiteashonraí a stóráil sna "
"clibeanna XMP agus IPTC. Is féidir luachanna an teimpléid a shocrú ar "
"leathanach cumraíochta an Teimpléid."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:85
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Face Tags (including face areas)"
msgstr "Clibeanna Aghaidhe (lena n-áirítear limistéir aghaidhe)"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:86
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to store face tags with face rectangles in the XMP tags."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun clibeanna aghaidhe le dronuilleoga aghaidhe a "
"stóráil sna clibeanna XMP."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:90
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Geolocation information (GPS)"
msgstr "Faisnéis gheo-shuímh (GPS)"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:91
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to store Geolocation information in the Exif tag and the "
"XMP tags."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun faisnéis Gheo-shuímh a stóráil sa chlib Exif agus "
"sna clibeanna XMP."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:115
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Reading and Writing Metadata"
msgstr "Meiteashonraí a Léamh agus a Scríobh"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:120
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Use ExifTool backend to read metadata from files"
msgstr "Bain úsáid as cúltaca ExifTool chun meiteashonraí a léamh ó chomhaid"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:121
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to read metadata from files with ExifTool backend "
"instead Exiv2. This will slowdown a little bit the synchronization of files "
"metadata with database."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun meiteashonraí a léamh ó chomhaid le cúltaca "
"ExifTool in ionad Exiv2. Cuirfidh sé seo moill bheag ar shioncrónú "
"meiteashonraí comhad leis an mbunachar sonraí."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:126
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Delegate to ExifTool backend all operations to write metadata to files"
msgstr ""
"Tarmlig do chúltaca ExifTool gach oibríocht chun meiteashonraí a scríobh "
"chuig comhaid"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:127
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to write metadata to files with ExifTool backend instead "
"Exiv2. This will slowdown a little bit the synchronization of files metadata "
"with database."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun meiteashonraí a scríobh chuig comhaid le cúltaca "
"ExifTool in ionad Exiv2. Cuirfidh sé seo moill bheag ar shioncrónú "
"meiteashonraí comhad leis an mbunachar sonraí."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:132
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Write metadata to DNG files"
msgstr "Scríobh meiteashonraí chuig comhaid DNG"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:133
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid "Turn on this option to write metadata into DNG files."
msgstr "Cas air an rogha seo chun meiteashonraí a scríobh i gcomhaid DNG."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:136
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "If possible write metadata to RAW files"
msgstr "Más féidir, scríobh meiteashonraí chuig comhaid AMH"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:137
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to write metadata into RAW files. This feature is "
"delegate to ExifTool backend and is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun meiteashonraí a scríobh i gcomhaid RAW. Déantar an "
"ghné seo a tharmligean chuig cúltaca ExifTool agus tá sí díchumasaithe de "
"réir réamhshocraithe."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:146
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Use lazy synchronization"
msgstr "Bain úsáid as sioncrónú leisciúil"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:148
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Instead of synchronizing metadata, just schedule it for synchronization."
"Synchronization can be done later by triggering the apply pending, or at "
"digikam exit"
msgstr ""
"In ionad meiteashonraí a shioncrónú, sceidealaigh é le haghaidh "
"sioncrónaithe. Is féidir sioncrónú a dhéanamh níos déanaí tríd an iarratas "
"ar feitheamh a spreagadh, nó ag imeacht digikam"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:152
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "&Update file modification timestamp when files are modified"
msgstr ""
"&Nuashonraigh stampa ama modhnaithe comhaid nuair a dhéantar comhaid a "
"mhodhnú"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:154
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn off this option to not update file timestamps when files are changed as "
"when you update metadata or image data. Note: disabling this option can "
"introduce some dysfunctions with applications which use file timestamps "
"properties to detect file modifications automatically."
msgstr ""
"Múch an rogha seo le gan stampaí ama comhad a nuashonrú nuair a athraítear "
"comhaid mar a tharlaíonn nuair a nuashonraítear meiteashonraí nó sonraí "
"íomhá. Tabhair faoi deara: d’fhéadfadh roinnt mífheidhmeanna a bheith mar "
"thoradh ar an rogha seo a dhíchumasú le feidhmchláir a úsáideann airíonna "
"stampaí ama comhad chun modhnuithe comhaid a bhrath go huathoibríoch."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:160
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "&Rescan file when files are modified"
msgstr "&Athscanadh an chomhaid nuair a dhéantar comhaid a mhodhnú"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:162
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turning this option on, will force digiKam to rescan files that has been "
"modified outside digiKam. If a file has changed it is file size or if the "
"last modified timestamp has changed, a rescan of that file will be performed "
"when digiKam starts."
msgstr ""
"Trí an rogha seo a chasadh air, cuirfidh sé iallach ar digiKam athscanadh a "
"dhéanamh ar chomhaid atá modhnaithe lasmuigh de digiKam. Má tá méid comhaid "
"athraithe nó má tá an stampa ama a modhnaíodh go deireanach athraithe, "
"déanfar athscanadh ar an gcomhad sin nuair a thosóidh digiKam."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:235
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Note: see %1 of ExifTool backend."
msgstr "Nóta: féach %1 de chúltaca ExifTool."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:237
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "write limitations"
msgstr "teorainneacha scríbhneoireachta"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:245
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid ""
"Note: these options depends of %1 availability. Check in the ExifTool tab "
"for details."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara: braitheann na roghanna seo ar infhaighteacht %1. Féach "
"sa chluaisín ExifTool le haghaidh sonraí."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_behavior.cpp:248
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "ExifTool backend"
msgstr "Cúltaca ExifTool"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_display.cpp:28
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Select Metadata Fields to be Displayed when using Custom Filters"
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh Réimsí Meiteashonraí le Taispeáint agus Scagairí Saincheaptha á n-"
"úsáid"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_display.cpp:43
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:tab"
msgid "Views"
msgstr "Radharcanna"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:31
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "When rotating a file"
msgstr "Agus comhad á rothlú"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:35
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio"
msgid "Rotate by only setting a flag"
msgstr "Rothlaigh trí bhratach a shocrú amháin"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:36
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio"
msgid "Rotate by changing the content if possible"
msgstr "Rothlaigh tríd an ábhar a athrú más féidir"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:37
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Even allow lossy rotation if necessary"
msgstr "Ceadaigh fiú rothlú caillteanach más gá"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:38
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Write flag to metadata if possible"
msgstr "Scríobh bratach chuig meiteashonraí más féidir"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:50
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Rotate files only by changing a flag, not touching the pixel data"
msgstr ""
"Rothlaigh comhaid trí bhratach a athrú amháin, gan teagmháil a dhéanamh leis "
"na sonraí picteilín"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:52
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<para>A file can be rotated in two ways:<nl/> You can change the contents, "
"rearranging the individual pixels of the image data.<nl/> Or you can set a "
"flag that the file is to be rotated before it is shown.</para> <para>Select "
"this option if you always want to set only a flag. This is less obtrusive, "
"but requires support if the file is accessed with another software. Ensure "
"to allow setting the flag in the metadata if you want to share your files "
"outside digiKam.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Is féidir comhad a rothlú ar dhá bhealach:<nl/> Is féidir leat an t-"
"ábhar a athrú, trí na picteilíní aonair de shonraí na híomhá a athchóiriú."
"<nl/> Nó is féidir leat bratach a shocrú go rothlófar an comhad sula "
"dtaispeántar é.</para> <para>Roghnaigh an rogha seo más mian leat bratach "
"amháin a shocrú i gcónaí. Tá sé seo níos lú treáite, ach teastaíonn "
"tacaíocht uaidh má dhéantar rochtain ar an gcomhad le bogearraí eile. "
"Cinntigh go gceadaítear an bhratach a shocrú sna meiteashonraí más mian leat "
"do chuid comhad a roinnt lasmuigh de digiKam.</para>"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:61
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "If possible rotate files by changing the pixel data"
msgstr "Más féidir, rothlaigh na comhaid trí na sonraí picteilíní a athrú"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:63
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<para>A file can be rotated in two ways:<nl/> You can change the contents, "
"rearranging the individual pixels of the image data.<nl/> Or you can set a "
"flag that the file is to be rotated before it is shown.</para> <para>Select "
"this option if you want the file to be rotated by changing the content. This "
"is a lossless operation for JPEG files. For other formats it is a lossy "
"operation, which you need to enable explicitly. It is not support for RAW "
"and other read-only formats, which will be rotated by flag only.</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Is féidir comhad a rothlú ar dhá bhealach:<nl/> Is féidir leat an t-"
"ábhar a athrú trí na picteilíní aonair de shonraí na híomhá a athchóiriú.<nl/"
"> Nó is féidir leat bratach a shocrú go bhfuil an comhad le rothlú sula "
"dtaispeántar é.</para> <para>Roghnaigh an rogha seo más mian leat an comhad "
"a rothlú tríd an ábhar a athrú. Is oibríocht gan chailliúint í seo do "
"chomhaid JPEG. I gcás formáidí eile, is oibríocht chaillteanach í, agus ní "
"mór duit í a chumasú go sainráite. Ní thacaítear le RAW ná le formáidí léite "
"amháin eile, a rothlófar le bratach amháin.</para>"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:73
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Rotate files by changing the pixel data even if the operation will incur "
"quality loss"
msgstr ""
"Rothlaigh comhaid trí na sonraí picteilíní a athrú fiú má chailltear "
"cáilíocht san oibríocht"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:75
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"For some file formats which apply lossy compression, data will be lost each "
"time the content is rotated. Check this option to allow lossy rotation. If "
"not enabled, these files will be rotated by flag."
msgstr ""
"I gcás roinnt formáidí comhaid a chuireann comhbhrú caillteanach i bhfeidhm, "
"caillfear sonraí gach uair a rothlaítear an t-ábhar. Seiceáil an rogha seo "
"chun rothlú caillteanach a cheadú. Mura bhfuil sé cumasaithe, rothlófar na "
"comhaid seo de réir bratach."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:81
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"When rotating a file by setting a flag, also change this flag in the file's "
"metadata"
msgstr ""
"Agus comhad á rothlú trí bhratach a shocrú, athraigh an bhratach seo i "
"meiteashonraí an chomhaid freisin"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:83
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"File metadata typically contains a flag describing that a file shall be "
"shown rotated. Enable this option to allow editing this field. "
msgstr ""
"De ghnáth bíonn bratach i meiteashonraí comhaid a mhíníonn go dtaispeánfar "
"comhad rothlaithe. Cumasaigh an rogha seo chun ligean don réimse seo a chur "
"in eagar. "

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:107
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option"
msgid "Show images/thumbnails &rotated according to orientation tag."
msgstr ""
"Taispeáin íomhánna/mionsamhlacha rothlaithe de &réir an chlib treoshuímh."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:109
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option"
msgid "Set orientation tag to normal after rotate/flip."
msgstr "Socraigh an clib treoshuímh go gnáth tar éis rothlú/smeach."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:120
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Note: These settings affect the album view and not the image editor. The "
"image editor always changes the image data during the rotation."
msgstr ""
"Nóta: Bíonn tionchar ag na socruithe seo ar radharc an albaim agus ní ar an "
"eagarthóir íomhá. Athraíonn an t-eagarthóir íomhá sonraí na híomhá i gcónaí "
"le linn an rothlaithe."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_rotation.cpp:134
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:tab"
msgid "Rotation"
msgstr "Rothlú"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:33
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Reading and Writing to Sidecars"
msgstr "Léamh agus Scríobh chuig Taobhcharranna"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:36
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Read from sidecar files"
msgstr "Léigh ó chomhaid taobhcharr"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:38
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to read metadata from XMP sidecar files when reading "
"metadata."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun meiteashonraí a léamh ó chomhaid taobhlíne XMP "
"agus meiteashonraí á léamh."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Write to sidecar files"
msgstr "Scríobh chuig comhaid taobhcharr"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:44
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to save, as specified, metadata to XMP sidecar files."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun meiteashonraí a shábháil, mar atá sonraithe, chuig "
"comhaid taobhlíne XMP."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:48
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item"
msgid "Write to XMP sidecar for read-only item only"
msgstr "Scríobh chuig XMP sidecar le haghaidh míre léite amháin"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:49
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item"
msgid "Write to XMP sidecar only"
msgstr "Scríobh chuig XMP sidecar amháin"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:50
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item"
msgid "Write to item and XMP Sidecar"
msgstr "Scríobh chuig mír agus XMP Sidecar"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:51
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid "Specify the exact mode of XMP sidecar writing"
msgstr "Sonraigh an modh cruinn scríbhneoireachta taobhlíne XMP"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:55
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Sidecar file names are compatible with commercial programs"
msgstr "Tá ainmneacha comhad taobhlíne comhoiriúnach le cláir tráchtála"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Turn on this option to create the XMP sidecar files with a compatible file "
"name (BASENAME.xmp) used by many commercial programs. For Darktable do not "
"enable this option."
msgstr ""
"Cas air an rogha seo chun na comhaid taobhlíne XMP a chruthú le hainm "
"comhaid comhoiriúnach (BASENAME.xmp) a úsáideann go leor clár tráchtála. I "
"gcás Darktable, ná cumasaigh an rogha seo."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:76
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Add file types to be recognised as sidecars.\n"
"digiKam (optionally) writes metadata to *.xmp sidecar files. Other programs "
"might use different types, which can be specified below. digiKam will "
"neither display these nor read from or write to them. But whenever a "
"matching album item (e.g. \"image.dng\" for \"image.dng.pp3\") is renamed, "
"moved, copied or deleted, the same operation will be done on these sidecar "
"files.\n"
"Multiple extensions must be separated by a semicolon or a space."
msgstr ""
"Cuir cineálacha comhaid leis le haithint mar chomhaid taobh.\n"
"Scríobhann digiKam (roghnach) meiteashonraí chuig comhaid taobh *.xmp. "
"D’fhéadfadh cláir eile cineálacha difriúla a úsáid, ar féidir iad a shonrú "
"thíos. Ní thaispeánfaidh digiKam iad seo ná ní léifidh sé uathu ná ní "
"scríobhfaidh sé chucu. Ach aon uair a athainmnítear, a bhogtar, a "
"chóipeáiltear nó a scriostar mír albaim chomhoiriúnach (m.sh. \"image.dng\" "
"le haghaidh \"image.dng.pp3\"), déanfar an oibríocht chéanna ar na comhaid "
"taobh seo.\n"
"Ní mór síntí iolracha a dheighilt le leathstad nó spás."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:91
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Here you can add extra extensions\n"
"of sidecars files to be processed alongside\n"
"regular items. These files will not be visible,\n"
"but regarded as an extension of the main file.\n"
"Just write \"xyz abc\" to support files with\n"
"the *.xyz and *.abc extensions. The internally\n"
"used sidecars type *.xmp is always included."
msgstr ""
"Anseo is féidir leat síntí breise a chur leis\n"
"de chomhaid taobhcharranna le próiseáil taobh le\n"
"míreanna rialta. Ní bheidh na comhaid seo le feiceáil,\n"
"ach measfar gur síneadh den phríomhchomhad iad.\n"
"Scríobh \"xyz abc\" chun tacú le comhaid leis na síntí \n"
"*.xyz agus *.abc. Cuirtear an cineál taobhcharranna\n"
"a úsáidtear go hinmheánach *.xmp san áireamh i gcónaí."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Enter additional sidecars file extensions."
msgstr "Cuir isteach síntí comhaid taobhcharranna breise."

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:102
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid "Additional &sidecar file extensions"
msgstr "Síntí comhaid &sidecar breise"

#: core/utilities/setup/metadata/setupmetadata_sidecars.cpp:117
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:tab"
msgid "Sidecars"
msgstr "Carranna taobh"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/ocvocldnntestdlg.cpp:83
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "AI GPU Test"
msgstr "Tástáil GPU Intleacht Shaorga"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/ocvocldnntestdlg.cpp:86
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"This will check if your system is able to use GPU acceleration\n"
"when running the AI models by validating OpenCV and OpenCL have the\n"
"required libraries and drivers installed.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to test your system now?"
msgstr ""

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/ocvocldnntestdlg.cpp:104
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button start the AI GPU test"
msgid "Start"
msgstr "Tosaigh"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/ocvocldnntestdlg.cpp:106
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button start the AI GPU test"
msgid "Begin test"
msgstr "Tosaigh an tástáil"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/ocvocldnntestdlg.cpp:142
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button start the AI GPU test"
msgid "Testing..."
msgstr "Tástáil..."

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/ocvocldnntestdlg.cpp:149
#, kde-format
msgid "Starting OpenCV OpenCL DNN test..."
msgstr "Ag tosú tástáil OpenCL DNN OpenCV..."

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/ocvocldnntestdlg.cpp:217
