#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:43
#, kde-format
msgid "&Scan for new items at startup"
msgstr "&Scanáil le haghaidh míreanna nua ag an am tosaithe"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:44
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set this option to force digiKam to scan all collections for new items to\n"
"register new elements in database. The scan is performed in the background "
"through\n"
"the progress manager available in the statusbar\n"
" when digiKam main interface\n"
"is loaded. If your computer is fast enough, this will have no effect on "
"usability\n"
"of digiKam while scanning. If your collections are huge or if you use a "
"remote database,\n"
"this can introduce low latency, and it is recommended to disable this option "
"and to plan\n"
"a manual scan through the maintenance tool at the right moment."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh an rogha seo chun digiKam a chur iallach gach bailiúchán a scanadh "
"le haghaidh\n"
"míreanna nua chun eilimintí nua a chlárú sa bhunachar sonraí. Déantar an "
"scanadh sa chúlra tríd an\n"
"bainisteoir dul chun cinn atá ar fáil sa bharra stádais\n"
" nuair a luchtaítear príomh-chomhéadan digiKam.\n"
"Mura bhfuil do ríomhaire tapa go leor, ní bheidh aon tionchar aige seo ar "
"inúsáidteacht\n"
"digiKam agus scanadh á dhéanamh. Má tá do bhailiúcháin ollmhór nó má "
"úsáideann tú bunachar sonraí iargúlta,\n"
"féadfaidh sé seo moill íseal a thabhairt isteach, agus moltar an rogha seo a "
"dhíchumasú agus scanadh láimhe a\n"
"phleanáil tríd an uirlis chothabhála ag an nóiméad ceart."

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:52
#, kde-format
msgid "Fast scan (detects new, deleted and renamed items)"
msgstr "Scanadh tapa (aimsíonn míreanna nua, scriosta agus athainmnithe)"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:53
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set this option to significantly speed up the scan. New items, deleted and "
"also\n"
"renamed items are found. In order to find items that have been changed, "
"this\n"
"option must be deactivated."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh an rogha seo chun an scanadh a bhrostú go suntasach. Aimsítear "
"míreanna nua, míreanna scriosta\n"
"agus míreanna athainmnithe freisin. Chun míreanna atá athraithe a aimsiú, ní "
"mór an rogha seo a\n"
"dhíghníomhachtú."

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:59
#, kde-format
msgid "Detect faces in newly added images"
msgstr "Aghaidheanna a bhrath in íomhánna nua-churtha leis"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:60
#, kde-format
msgid "Enable background face recognition scan"
msgstr "Cumasaigh scanadh aitheantais aghaidhe sa chúlra"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:61
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set this option to automatically start a background face recognition scan\n"
"when a new face is tagged. This will make the tagging process easier."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh an rogha seo chun scanadh aitheantais aghaidhe cúlra a thosú go "
"huathoibríoch\n"
"nuair a dhéantar clib ar aghaidh nua. Déanfaidh sé seo an próiseas clibeála "
"níos éasca."

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:64
#, kde-format
msgid "Remove obsolete core database objects"
msgstr "Bain réada bunachar sonraí croí atá as dáta"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:65
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set this option to force digiKam to clean up the core database from obsolete "
"item entries.\n"
"Entries are only deleted if the connected image/video/audio file was already "
"removed, i.e.\n"
"the database object wastes space.\n"
"This option does not clean up other databases as the thumbnails or "
"recognition db.\n"
"For clean up routines for other databases, please use the maintenance."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh an rogha seo chun digiKam a chur iallach an bunachar sonraí lárnach "
"a ghlanadh ó iontrálacha míreanna atá as dáta.\n"
"Ní scriostar iontrálacha ach amháin má baineadh an comhad íomhá/físe/fuaime "
"ceangailte cheana féin, i.e.\n"
"má chuireann an réad bunachar sonraí amú spás.\n"
"Ní ghlanann an rogha seo bunachair shonraí eile mar na mionsamhlacha nó an "
"bunachar sonraí aitheantais.\n"
"Le haghaidh gnáthaimh ghlantacháin do bhunachair shonraí eile, bain úsáid as "
"an gcothabháil."

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:73
#, kde-format
msgid "Confirm when moving items to the &trash"
msgstr "Deimhnigh nuair a bhogtar míreanna chuig an &bruscar"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:74
#, kde-format
msgid "Confirm when permanently deleting items"
msgstr "Deimhnigh nuair a scriostar míreanna go buan"

#: core/utilities/setup/misc/setupmisc_behavior.cpp:75
#, kde-format
